Umubare wiyongereye cyane w'indwara ya Koronavirusi (COVID-19) mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere k'ubukungu k'Uburayi n'Ubwongereza, kuva ku wa 1 Mutarama kugeza ku wa 15 Werurwe 2020
Umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 ugenda wiyongera ugaragaza imiterere nk'iyo mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza, ibyo bikaba byerekana ko nubwo iki cyorezo cya COVID-19 kigenda kirushaho kwiyongera mu bihugu byose, nubwo kigenda gitandukana bitewe n'igihugu.
Dukurikije ubunararibonye bw'Ubutaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibyumba by'ubuvuzi by'indembe bigomba kongera ubushake bwo kwitegura umubare wiyongera w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bazakenera kwitabwaho, cyane cyane mu by'ubuvuzi bw'indembe.
Ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, havuzwe ko hari abantu benshi banduye indwara y'ibicurane by'uburwayi butaramenyekana mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara cyavuze ko icyateye iyo ndwara ari virusi ya corona nshya, ubu yitwa SARS-CoV-2.
Kuva icyo gihe, indwara iterwa n'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 yiswe indwara ya virusi ya corona (COVID-19).
Kugeza ubu, ibihamya bigaragaza ko abantu bagera kuri 80% banduye COVID-19 barwaye indwara yoroheje; ni ukuvuga ko bafite ubwandu bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero bufite ibimenyetso cyangwa budafite, kandi abenshi muri bo barakira.
Hafi 14% by'abanduye COVID-19 barushijeho kuremba, bituma baba bakeneye kuvurirwa mu bitaro, mu gihe abasigaye 6% bafite indwara ikomeye, bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane.
Imibare y'abapfuye mu barwayi bari mu bitaro kubera COVID-19 yari hafi 4%.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, twasuzumye imiterere y'umubare w'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 muri buri gihugu cyo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere k'ubukungu k'Uburayi (EU/EEA) n'Ubwongereza (UK) maze tugereranya n'uw'intara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Turasuzuma kandi umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 muri EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza n'uw'u Butaliyani hagati ya 31 Mutarama na 15 Werurwe 2020.
Abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza
Nyuma y'ibyabaye mu Bushinwa, COVID-19 ikomeje gukwirakwira mu karere, kandi ikomeje gukwirakwira mu bindi bihugu byo ku isi.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Umuyobozi Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Mu nomero ya Eurosurvivals yo ku ya 5 Werurwe 2020, Spiteri n'abandi batangaje ko ari bo bantu ba mbere bemejwe ko banduye COVID-19 mu Burayi nk'uko bitangazwa n'ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima.
Mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu k'Uburayi, abantu batatu ba mbere bemejwe n'u Bufaransa batangajwe ku itariki ya 24 Mutarama 2020 bavuye i Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, abantu banduye COVID-19 bari mu bihugu byose 30 bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Umurenge w'Ubukungu w'u Burayi n'Ubwongereza (Ubwongereza), aho kuva ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 kugeza uyu munsi, hamaze kuvugwa abantu 39,768 banduye ndetse n'abapfuye 1,727 mu gihe mu Butaliyani honyine hamaze kuvugwa abantu 17,750 banduye ndetse n'abapfuye 1,441.
Kubona umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 n'umubare w'abanduye
Mu Kigo cy'u Burayi Gishinzwe Kurwanya Indwara no Kuzirinda (ECDC), imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 muri buri gihugu ku isi yose, iboneka gusa mu bikoresho byemewe n'amategeko, urugero nk'ubushikiranganji bw'ubuzima bw'icyo gihugu, inzego z'ubuzima z'igihugu n'akarere n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima, ihora ivugururwa buri munsi saa munani za mu gitondo.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu gupima imiterere ya COVID-19 mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere k'ubukungu k'Uburayi n'u Bwongereza no kuyigereranya n'iy'u Butaliyani.
Nk'igipimo cy'ubwiyongere bw'abanduye COVID-19, twabaze umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 mu minsi 14, hanyuma dufata icyerekezo cy'indwara ya COVID-19 mu bihugu byose bigize EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza hagati ya 1 Mutarama na 15 Werurwe 2020.
Nanone kandi, twatanze umubare munini w'ubwandu bw'icyorezo bwavuzwe mu bihugu byose guhera ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020 saa munani za mu gitondo, tugereranyije n'umubare w'ubwandu bw'icyorezo mu Butaliyani hagati ya tariki ya 31 Mutarama na 15 Werurwe 2020.
Uko COVID-19 imeze mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza
Imibare y'ubwandu bw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere ka Afurika y'Iburengerazuba n'Ubwongereza, yakurikiwe n'iy'abari mu ntara ya Hubei (Ubushinwa) (Igishushanyo cya 1).
Ku muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere k'ubukungu k'Uburayi n'u Bwongereza muri rusange, umubare w'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 watangiye kwiyongera ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, hanyuma wiyongera cyane ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 (Icyigisho cy'inyongera).
Ibi byatewe ahanini n'ubwiyongere bwihuse bw'abanduye muri Italiya, ariko ibihugu byose bigize EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza byagaragaje ko umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 wiyongereye cyane (Ibipimo by'inyongera).
Igishushanyo cya 2 kigaragaza umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere ka Burayi k'Ubukungu n'Ubwongereza ugereranyije n'uw'u Butaliyani kuva ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Yagaragaje ko guhera ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe saa munani za mu gitondo, ibindi bihugu 15 byo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere k'ubukungu k'Uburayi n'Ubwongereza byatangaje umubare w'abanduye mu buryo bwuzuye nk'uko byari bimeze mu Butaliyani mu byumweru bitatu gusa cyangwa munsi y'aho.
Ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bwacu bigaragaza ko umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 wiyongera cyane mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere k'ubukungu bw'Uburayi n'u Bwongereza.
Imiterere igaragara mu mubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 igaragaza ko icyorezo kirimo kwiyongera ku buryo bwihuse mu bihugu byose.
Ibi ni nubwo ibihugu biri mu byiciro bitandukanye, kandi n'ubwo ibisubizo by'ubuzima rusange mu bihugu bitandukanye, ibisobanuro by'uburwayi mu bihugu bitandukanye n'amabwiriza agenga abagerageza COVID-19, harimo n'ibipimo byo gukurikirana, bishobora gutandukana.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu turere tw'u Butaliyani twibasiwe n'iki cyorezo bavuze ko abagera kuri 10% by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane, kandi amakuru agera ku bakuru b'itangazamakuru avuga ko ibitaro n'ibyumba by'ubuvuzi muri utwo turere byamaze kugera ku kigero cyabyo.
Kugeza ubu, amakuru ku byerekeranye no kujya mu bitaro no mu bigo byita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere k'ubukungu k'Uburayi, araboneka ku bantu 6% na 1% by'abarwayi (amakuru ntagaragara).
Icyakora, bigomba gukusanywa mu buryo bufite gahunda kugira ngo byuzuze amakuru y'ubugenzuzi, yibanda ku mubare w'abamaze kwandura n'abapfuye.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 201011 bwagaragaje itandukaniro rinini mu kuboneka kw'ibitanda by'ubuvuzi bw'imbaraga n'ubwitonzi mu Burayi, hagati ya 29.2 mu Budage na 4.2 ku bantu 100.000 muri Porutugali.
Ibi bivuze ko ibihugu bishobora kuba bifite umutungo munini cyangwa muke ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani (12.5 ibitanda by'ubuvuzi bw'indembe n'ubwiteganyirize ku bantu 100,000 mu 2010).
Imiterere y'ibimenyetso by'imiterere y'ubuvuzi, hamwe n'ingero z'igihugu kimwe cya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza ku byerekeye umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 bari mu bitaro bafite ibyago byo kurenga 90% by'ubuvuzi bw'indembe, biboneka mu isesengura rya gatandatu ry'igenzura ry'ibyago byihutirwa bya COVID-19 ryakozwe n'Ikigo cy'u Burayi gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara.
Kubera ko kugeza ubu, abarwayi bakusanyirijwe mu turere tw'ibihugu bigize EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza, kandi ibitaro n'ibyumba by'ubuvuzi bikunze gukorera mu turere tw'abaturage, ni byiza ko amakuru y'abarwayi n'ibitanda by'ubuvuzi by'akarere byatangwa ku rwego rw'amazina y'ibyumba by'ubuvuzi by'akarere 2 (NUTS-2).
Ibyaranze Ubutaliyani n'imiterere iriho mu bindi bihugu bigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 kirimo kwiyongera mu buryo bwihuse mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'ubukungu k'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza.
Ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi ba SARS-CoV-2 bigomba kwitegura uburyo bwo gukwirakwiza SARS-CoV-2 mu baturage, kandi bikongera umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho, cyane cyane kwitabwaho cyane, nk'uko bigenda mu bice byugarijwe n'iki cyorezo mu Butaliyani.
