Izo sitokine zituma ingirabuzimafatizo z'umubiri zitanga imizi myinshi cyane, kandi ni zo zitera indwara yo guhumeka nabi cyane n'izindi ndwara ziterwa n'imyanya y'umubiri.
Gukumira ubwirinzi bw'umubiri ni ngombwa mu kuvura ibihuha bya sitokine, cyane cyane mu barwayi bakomeye.
Hari imiti ya hormone z'ubushakashatsi, tosilezumab, na antibody ya interleukin 6, yakoreshejwe mu kuvura cytocin storm.
Ubundi buvuzi bwo kurwanya cytocin storm burimo guhindura imikorere y'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri buyobowe na T-cells; IFN-γ, IL-1, na TNF block; Janus kinase inhibition; Plennatumumab; cytokine signal block 4; na histone desictilis inhibitors.
Imiti yo guhangana n'uburwayi n'imiti yo kurwanya indwara z'uburwayi yakoreshejwe cyane mu kuvura SARS kugira ngo igabanye ubukana bw'ingaruka ziterwa n'uburwayi.
Icyakora, imiti yo mu rwego rwo hejuru ntiyafashije cyane abarwayi ba SARS na COVID-19 bafite uburwayi bukomeye bw'ibihaha.
Ahubwo, bishobora gutera ibindi bimenyetso bikomeye, cyane cyane imitsi y'amagufa, bigira ingaruka zikomeye ku buryo indwara ishobora gukwirakwira.
Icyakora, gukoreshwa k'imizunguruko migufi y'imiti ikurura imisemburo mu rugero ruto cyane no mu rugero ruciriritse, byasabwe ku barwayi ba COVID-19 bafite ibibazo bikomeye.
Mu gihe twandikaga iyi nkuru, nta muti wa virusi wigeze ugaragazwa ko ugira ingaruka nziza.
Nyamara, byaje kugaragara ko guterwa umuti wa Remdesivir, ari wo mugereranya wa nucleotide, mu maraso, byagize ingaruka nziza ku murwayi wa COVID-19 wo muri Amerika.
Remdecivir ni umuti uvura virusi nshya watangijwe na Gilead mu buryo bw'ibanze mu kuvura indwara ziterwa na virusi za Ebola na Marburg.
Nyuma yaho, Remdesivir yagaragaje ko ishobora kubuza izindi virusi zifite ADN-ribose imwe, harimo za MERS na SARS.
Hashingiwe kuri izo virusi, Gilead yatanze iki gikoresho mu Bushinwa kugira ngo gikoreshwe mu kugerageza abantu banduye SARS-CoV-2, kandi turategereje cyane ko haboneka ibisubizo.
Byongeye kandi, parisetinib, interverone-alpha, lupinavir/ritonavir, na ribavirin, byashyizwe ahagaragara nk'imiti ishobora gukoreshwa mu barwayi bafite ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero bikaze.
Gufata umuti wa Blupenavir/Ritonavir bishobora gutuma umuntu agira igifu, kuribwa, kuruka, gukomereka kw'umura n'ibindi bibazo.
Uburyo izo miti zikorana n'izindi miti zikoreshwa ku barwayi bugomba kugenzurwa cyane.
Plasma y'abarwayi bakize, no kubyara udukoko tw'ubumara.
Gukuza amaraso y'abarwayi bakize indwara kugira ngo bavurwe n'abandi barwayi bafite iyo ndwara cyangwa se kugira ngo abantu bafite amagara mazima badakwirakwizwa indwara, bifite amateka maremare.
Koko rero, abarwayi bakize akenshi baba bafite ibice byinshi by'umubiri w'umurwayi mu maraso yabo.
Antibodies ni globulines z'ubwirinzi bwa Ig (AIG) ziterwa na bactérium lymphocyte mu kurwanya imikorere y'ibinyabutabire n'ibindi bintu by'amahanga, kandi zikamenya molekile zidasanzwe mu byorezo kandi zikayivanga.
Hashingiwe kuri ibyo, plasma yakuwe mu maraso y'abarwayi bakize COVID-19 maze bayishyira mu barwayi 10 bafite ibibazo bikomeye.
Ibimenyetso byabo byagiye bihinduka mu masaha 24, biherekejwe no kugabanuka kw'uburwayi, kugabanuka kw'umuriro wa virusi no kuzamuka k'umwuka wa ogisijeni mu maraso.
Icyakora, kugira ngo ubwo buryo bukoreshwe mu buryo bwagutse mbere yo kubona umuti wihariye, bisaba ko hagira ibihamya n'ibisobanuro.
Byongeye kandi, bitewe n'ingaruka zo kuvura, hari ibindi bintu by'ingaruka bigomba kwitabwaho.
Urugero, abarwayi bashobora gutuma abarwayi bagira ingufu nyinshi cyane, bigatuma bagira indwara yo kurekura sitokina, ishobora no kuba ari uburozi bwica.
Ubusanzwe, amaraso aba afite ibice bike by'abakoraho iyo ndwara, kandi abarwayi bafite ibibazo bikomeye baba bakeneye cyane amaraso.
Biragoye guhanga udukoko tw'ubwirinzi tw'ubwoko butandukanye no kubuhinga mu buryo bwihuse bihagije kugira ngo twirinde icyorezo cyugarije isi yose.
Ku bw'ibyo, gutandukanya ingirabuzimafatizo z'abarwayi bakize no kumenya kode z'imiterere y'umubiri zigaragaza ko hari abaturwanya, cyangwa gusuzuma abaturwanya bakoresheje poroteyine z'ingenzi za virusi, ni byo byoroshye kandi birakwiriye.
Muri ubwo buryo, dushobora kongera cyane ingirabuzimafatizo.
Ubuvuzi gakondo bw'Abashinwa bwakoreshwaga mu kuvura indwara zitandukanye mu Bushinwa mu gihe cy'imyaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi.
Nyamara, ingaruka zayo zishingiye cyane ku bintu byinshi mu buryo butandukanye bitewe n'indwara umuntu yanduye, hashingiwe ku bitekerezo by'ubuvuzi gakondo bw'Abashinwa.
Ibyinshi mu bintu bikora bikomeza kuba ibimuri ku mutima cyangwa bidafite aho bihuriye n'uko bikora, kubera ko bitoroshye kubimenya no kumenya neza ibyo bikora cyangwa se uburyo bwiza cyane bwo kubikora.
Muri iki gihe, kubera ko nta muti wihariye na wa COVID-19 uhari, imiti gakondo y'Abashinwa yabaye imwe mu miti y'ingenzi yafasha abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje cyangwa bito cyangwa abakize indwara zikomeye.
Urugero, udupfunyika twa Shu Feng Ji Do na Lian Hua King Wen twabonetse ko dufite akamaro mu kuvura COVID-19.
Ibipimo byo gukira cyane by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 byabonetse mu ntara nyinshi zo mu Bushinwa zakoresheje imiti gakondo y'Abashinwa ku barwayi 87% barimo Gansu (63.7%), Ningxia (50%), na Hunan (50%), mu gihe intara ya Hubei, yakoresheje imiti gakondo y'Abashinwa gusa ku barwayi ba COVID-19 bagera kuri 30%, yari ifite igipimo cyo gukira kiri hasi cyane (13%).
Icyakora, ibyo ni ugereranya gusa, kuko hari ibindi bintu byinshi bigomba kugenzurwa, urugero nk'umubare w'abarwayi n'uburemere bw'uburwayi bwabo.
Ku ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, Polly Chang n'abo bakoranaga basohoye ubushakashatsi bugereranya imiti y'ab'iburengerazuba (WM) yonyine n'iy'ab'iburengerazuba n'iy'abashinwa.
Basanze igihe cyo gukira ubushyuhe bukabije, kudahita ugira ibimenyetso, no kuguma mu bitaro ari gito cyane mu itsinda ry'abaganga bo mu Burengerazuba n'abari mu itsinda ry'abaganga bo mu Bushinwa, ugereranyije n'abari mu itsinda ry'abaganga bo mu Burengerazuba gusa.
Igitangaje cyane, ni uko igipimo cy'ubwiyongere bw'ibimenyetso (gitarenze gato kugeza ku ndwara ikomeye) cyari gito cyane mu itsinda ry'ubuvuzi bw'uburengerazuba + umuganga w'umwimerere w'Abashinwa ugereranyije n'itsinda ry'ubuvuzi bw'uburengerazuba gusa (7.4% kuri 46.2%), kandi igipimo cy'urupfu cyari gito mu itsinda ry'ubuvuzi bw'uburengerazuba + umuganga w'umwimerere w'Abashinwa ugereranyije n'itsinda ry'ubuvuzi bw'uburengerazuba gusa (8.8% kuri 39%).
Icyakora, ubufasha n'umutekano by'imiti gakondo y'Abashinwa biracyategereje ko hakorwa ibindi bigeragezo by'ubushakashatsi ku rugero rwagutse, mu bigo byinshi.
Nanone kandi, birashishikaje gusobanura uburyo bukora, no gusobanura ibirimo cyangwa se uko bikoreshwa mu buvuzi bwa gakondo bw'Abashinwa.
Abarwayi bakekwaho cyangwa bemejwe ko bafite COVID-19 akenshi bagira ubwoba bwinshi bwo kurwara indwara yandura cyane ndetse ishobora no kubaca, kandi abantu bari mu kato bumva barambiwe, bafite irungu, kandi bafite umujinya.
Byongeye kandi, ibimenyetso by'ubwandu, urugero nk'ibicurane, kubura umwuka wa ogisijeni, gukorora, hamwe n'ingaruka mbi z'imiti, urugero nk'ibitotsi biterwa n'imiti ituma umuntu agira imisemburo, bishobora gutuma arushaho guhangayika no guhungabana.
Mu cyiciro cya mbere cy'icyorezo cya SARS, havugwa indwara zitandukanye zo mu mutwe zirimo indwara z'agahinda gakabije, guhangayika, guhungabana, guhuzagurika, ibimenyetso by'indwara zo mu mutwe, uburwayi bwo mu mutwe ndetse n'ubwiyahura.
Gukurikirana no kwigunga by'agateganyo, nk'igice cy'ibisubizo by'ubuzima rusange ku cyorezo cya COVID-19, bishobora gutuma abantu barushaho guhangayika no kumva ko bafite icyaha ku ngaruka z'ubwandu, kwigunga no gusebya umuryango n'inshuti zabo.
Ku bw'ibyo, abantu barwaye COVID-19, abantu bakekwaho kuyandura, abantu bahuye na bo, ndetse n'abandi bantu bose babikeneye, bagomba guhabwa ubufasha mu by'ubuzima bwo mu mutwe.
Ubufasha bw'imitekerereze bugomba kuba bukubiyemo gushyiraho amatsinda y'ubuzima bwo mu mutwe y'indangagaciro zitandukanye, guhuza abantu mu buryo bwumvikana neza kugira ngo bagire amakuru ajyanye n'icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 n'uburyo bwo kucyitwaramo, no gukoresha ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki by'imiti n'ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga kugira ngo birinde guhangana.
Inkingo zifite ubushobozi bwo guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'iyo virusi kuva mu nyamaswa n'abantu byanduye kugeza ku barwayi bayirwara, ni ngombwa kandi akenshi zirimo gukoreshwa mu kurwanya indwara ziterwa n'imikorere y'ubwandu.
Hari hashyizweho imihati yo gukora inkingo zishingiye kuri poroteyine S kugira ngo haboneke abarwayi b'umubiri batagira aho bahurira n'indwara ya SARS-CoV-2 kandi bakagira imbaraga mu gihe kirekire.
Inkingo z'ubuzima z'ibinyabutabire zasuzumwe mu ngero z'amatungo zo kuvura SARS.
Icyakora, ubushobozi bw'izo nkingo z'abazunguzayi mu bantu bakuru n'abashya mu buryo bw'ibyago n'uburyo bwo kwirinda kwandura virusi y'ibanze y'amatungo, ntibwari bwaramenyekanye mbere y'uko hatangira igeragezwa ry'ubuvuzi.
Ibyo bishobora kuba biterwa n'uko SARS imaze imyaka 17 itarangira, kandi kuva icyo gihe nta muntu mushya wongeye kwandura.
Mu buryo bunyuranye n'ibyo, abantu benshi banduye MERS mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati bakomeje kugaragara kandi bakwirakwira mu tundi turere kubera ko inyamaswa zikomeje kuboneka mu turere twugarijwe n'icyorezo.
Uburyo bwo kwirinda MERS bwakoreshwaga mu gukoresha virusi idakora, ADN-ribose-deoxygenated plasmides, virus transporters, nanoparticles, virus-like particles, na subunites z'uruhu rw'umushongi, bimwe muri byo byasuzumwe mu ngero z'inyamaswa.
Guteza imbere urukingo rukomeye kandi rukomeye rwa SARS-CoV-2 ku bantu badafite ubwirinzi ni inshingano yihutirwa kandi y'ingenzi mu kugenzura icyorezo kiriho.
Nyamara, gutsinda iki kibazo ni ikibazo gikomeye bitewe n'igihe kirekire (kimwe cya mezi 18) gikenewe mu gukora urukingo n'impinduka z'imiterere ya virusi ya corona.
COVID-19, nk'indwara nshya, itangiye kwerekana uburyo bwayo bwose bwo kuvura mu barwayi babarirwa mu bihumbi.
Mu bihe byinshi, abarwayi bashobora gukira buhoro buhoro nta bihano.
Nyamara, COVID-19, kimwe na SARS na MERS, na yo ifitanye isano n'ubwiyongere bw'uburwayi n'urupfu rwinshi mu barwayi bakomeye.
Ku bw'ibyo, kubaka uburyo bwo kwitegura indwara ni ngombwa ku bigo by'ubuzima kugira ngo bishyire mu mwanya wa mbere serivisi zabo, cyane cyane mu turere dufite amikoro make.
Dushingiye ku bipimo by'ubuvuzi byatangajwe kugeza ubu, ibi bikurikira bishobora kugira ingaruka ku byiringiro by'uko abarwayi ba COVID-19 bazagenda barwara cyangwa bikaba bifitanye isano na byo (Igishushanyo (Igishushanyo cya 33)):
Imyaka: Imyaka ni yo yari ingenzi cyane mu kumenya uko SARS izagenda, kandi ni na ko bimeze kuri COVID-19.
Abantu bafite imyaka iri hagati ya 30 na 65 ni bo bagaragaye ko banduye cyane COVID-19, aho 47.7% by'aba barwaye barengeje imyaka 50 mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bantu 8,866 nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru.
Abarwayi bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane bari bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara z'ibanze n'ibibazo by'indwara kandi bari bakuze cyane kurusha abatari babikeneye (hagati y'imyaka 66 na 51), ibyo bikaba byerekana ko imyaka ari yo igena uko abarwayi ba COVID-19 bazagaragara.
Igitsina: SARS-CoV-2 ibasira abagabo benshi kurusha abagore (0.31/100.000 kuri 0.27/100.000), nk'uko byagaragajwe haruguru.
Indwara ziterwa n'indwara z'umutima: Abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane baba bafite ibyago byinshi byo guhura n'indwara z'umutima zikomeye n'umutima udakora neza.
Indwara z'umutima ni na zo zatumaga abantu benshi bapfa bitewe na SARS.
Bivugwa ko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora no guhuza ingirabuzimafatizo z'umura n'injyenzyme ihindura angiotensin 2, ibyo bikaba byatera ibibazo by'imirire y'umura mu barwayi ba COVID-19.
Ni iby'ingenzi ko tumenya ko imyaka n'indwara z'inkomoko bifitanye isano rya bugufi, kandi ko bishobora no kurenga ku rugero rumwe.
Ibisubizo by'ibizamini bidasanzwe: Uburemere bwa poroteyine C (CRP) mu maraso bugaragaza ubukana bw'ubwandu cyangwa ubwandu bw'uruhu, kandi byatangajwe ko ari ikintu cyerekana indwara, ibisubizo ku miti, n'ukuntu umuntu azakira.
Nanone kandi, hari abavuze ko hari isano hagati y'uburemere bwa C-reactive n'uburemere bw'indwara ya COVID-19 n'uko umuntu ashobora kubaho.
Uretse ibyo, ingano yo hejuru ya enzyme ituma intungamubiri z'umuntu zitera amavuta (LDH), aspartate amine transporter (AST), alanine amine transporter (ALT), na creatine kinase (CK) na zo zishobora gufasha mu guhanura ingaruka.
Izo enzymes ziboneka cyane mu bice byinshi by'umubiri, cyane cyane mu mutima no mu gifu, kandi zirakurwaho mu gihe hari imikorere mibi y'umubiri.
Ni ibimenyetso bisanzwe bigaragaza ko umutima cyangwa impyiko bitagikora neza.
Ibimenyetso by'ingenzi: Imyitozo ngororamubiri y'igituza n'iterambere ry'ibimenyetso by'igituza bigomba gufatwa hamwe n'ibindi bibazo kugira ngo hategerezwe ingaruka za COVID-19 n'ingaruka zayo.
Gukoresha imiti yo kuvura: Nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru, imiti yo kuvura ni imiti yo kuvura ikoreshwa cyane mu kuvura indwara zandura kugira ngo igabanye ubukana bw'ingaruka ziterwa n'uburwayi.
Kuva hakoreshwa cyane imiti ya hormone zongera imikorere mu barwayi ba SARS, abenshi mu barokotse indwara ya myeloidose barwaye ubumuga bw'igihe kirekire kandi ubuzima bwabo bukaba budafite ireme.
Ku bw'ibyo, imiti yo mu rwego rwo hasi kandi y'igihe gito igomba gukoreshwa mu barwayi ba COVID-19, niba ari ngombwa.
Imihangayiko yo mu mutwe: Nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru, mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19, abarwayi benshi bagize imihangayiko idasanzwe; akenshi bakomeje kwihanganira igihe kirekire cyo kwigunga, kubura icyizere, no kubona abagize umuryango wabo na bagenzi babo barwaye bapfa.
Ni ngombwa gutanga inama z'ubuvuzi n'ubufasha burambye kugira ngo aba barwayi bashobore gukira stress no gusubira mu buzima busanzwe.
Dukurikije ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bantu kugeza ubu, COVID-19 isa n'aho ifite ibimenyetso bitandukanye n'iby'icyorezo cya SARS.
Usibye kongera kubyara mu bwonko bwo hasi, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kongera kubyara neza mu bwonko bwo hejuru kandi igatera ibimenyetso byoroheje cyangwa nta bimenyetso mu cyiciro cya mbere cy'ubwandu, kimwe n'izindi koronavirusi zitera imbeho.
Ku bw'ibyo, abarwayi banduye mu gihe cy'uburwayi bwa mbere cyangwa mu gihe cyo kurera bashobora gukora virusi nyinshi mu gihe cy'ibikorwa bya buri munsi, bigatuma kurwanya icyorezo bitoroha.
Nyamara, abantu batekerezaga ko kwandura SARS-CoVs biba mu gihe abarwayi barwaye cyane, mu gihe benshi batanduraga virusi hakiri kare.
Bityo, icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiriho ubu kirakomeye cyane kandi kiragoye cyane kugenzura kurusha icyorezo cya SARS.
Muri iki gihe, mu Bushinwa hari ibikorwa by'ingufu, harimo gufunga Wuhan n'imigi ihakikije no gushyira abantu bose mu kato mu byiringiro byo kubuza ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2.
Nubwo izi ngamba zagize ingaruka zikomeye ku bukungu n'ibindi bice by'igihugu, umubare w'abarwayi bashya uragenda ugabanuka, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko icyorezo cyagabanutse.
Igishishikaje ni uko iki cyorezo kizarangira muri Werurwe, kandi ko kizakomeza kugabanuka mu gihe cy'amezi 3 cyangwa 4.
Icyakora, hari abandi bahanga badafite icyizere nk'icyo.
Paul Hunter n'abandi bagereranyije ko COVID-19, isa n'iyandura cyane kurusha SARS, itazarangira mu 2020.
Ira Longini n'abandi bakoze uburyo bwo guhanura ingaruka z'icyorezo, bavuga ko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwandura bibiri bya gatatu by'abatuye isi.
Itsinda ryo muri Kanada ryavuze ko SARS-CoV-2 yagaragaye mu bipimo by'ibinyamushongo n'amarira y'abarwayi bakize bavuye mu bitaro mu byumweru bibiri bishize, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko virusi nshya ishobora kuba ari indwara ihoraho isa n'iy'ibicurane.
Nyamara, hari ibimenyetso by'uko mu Bushinwa hazabaho ubwandu bushya bugabanuka, bigaragaza ko ingamba ziriho zishobora kuba zagize icyo zigeraho.
Mu mizo ya mbere, byari byitezwe ko Ebola ishobora gutera abantu bagera kuri miriyoni, ikazahitana abantu bagera kuri miriyoni.
Nyamara, indwara yaje kugenzurwa hakurikijwe ingamba zikomeye zo gushyira abantu mu kato no kubacungira ukwa bonyine.
Kimwe na SARS-CoV, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kuba ifite ubushobozi buke bwo gutera indwara, amaherezo ikazavanwaho cyangwa ikaba virusi idakwirakwira cyane ikanabana n'abantu.
Ku bijyanye n'icyorezo cya COVID-19 cy'indwara ya SARS na MERS, biri hasi aha (Igishushanyo 55).
SARS-CoV-2 yandura cyane mu gihe umuntu akoroye cyangwa atemye, kandi ishobora kwandura binyuze mu guhura n'ibintu byanduye virusi.
Nanone, basanze virusi mu byondo, ibyo bikaba byerekana ko ishobora gukwirakwira mu kanwa.
Ubushakashatsi buherutse gukorwa ku bantu 138 bwagaragaje ko 41% by'abo bantu bashobora kuba barandura mu bitaro, harimo abarwayi 17 bari bafite izindi ndwara kandi 40 ari abavuzi.
Niyo mpamvu, ingamba zikomeye zigomba gufatwa kugira ngo abantu barinde, cyane cyane abavura, abafasha abantu, abagize umuryango, abo bakorana ndetse n'abahitaga bahuye n'abarwayi cyangwa abantu banduye.
Kwambara udupfukamunwa ni yo ntambwe ya mbere yo kwirinda ishobora gukoreshwa mu kugabanya ibyago byo kwandura; gukoresha udupfukamunwa two kubaga n'udupfukamunwa two guhumeka N95 (urukurikirane rw'imyaka ya 1860) bifasha mu kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'ubwandu.
Udupfukamunwa two kubaga tubuza udutonyanga tw'amazi duva ku muntu ushobora kuba yaranduye kwanduzwa n'umwuka cyangwa ku bintu, aho dushobora kuzajya tugeza ku bandi.
Nyamara, udupfukamunwa twa N95 (umurongo wa 1860s) gusa dushobora kurinda guterwa na feryoni nto cyane kuva kuri 10 kugeza kuri 80 nanometero, gusa 5% gusa ya feryoni ishobora kwinjira mu buryo bwuzuye; SARS-CoV-2 isa na SARS-CoV mu bunini kandi ifite ubunini bwa 85 nanometero buri.
Kubera ko utwo duce dushobora kwinjira mu myenda itanu yabaga yashyizwe hamwe, abashinzwe ubuzima bazajya bahura n'abarwayi bagomba kwambara udupfukamunwa N95 (urukurikirane rw'ibya 1860), ariko ntibagomba kwambara udupfukamunwa twabaga twashyizwe hamwe.
Uretse udupfukamunwa, abashinzwe ubuzima bagomba kwambara imyenda ikumira abantu kugira ngo bakomeze kugabanya cyane cyane guhura na virusi.
Virusi zishobora kandi kwanduza umuntu binyuze mu maso.
Ku ya 22 Mutarama 2020, umuganga yafashwe na SARS-CoV-2 nubwo yari yambaye agapfukamunwa ka N95; birashoboka ko virusi yinjiye mu mubiri we binyuze mu maso ye yahiye.
Ku bw'ibyo, abatanga serivisi z'ubuzima bagomba kandi kwambara udukingirizo cyangwa amadarubindi mu gihe bakorana n'abarwayi.
Ku bantu bose bari mu turere twugarijwe n'icyorezo cyangwa dushobora kugiti cyacyo, basabwa gukaraba intoki kenshi cyane bakoresheje isabune, kugerageza kuguma mu rugo kugira ngo bakore isuku no kugabanya imikoranire n'abantu bashobora kuba barwaye.
Abantu bashobora gutandukana n'umurwayi mu gihe bari mu ntera ya metero eshatu.
Izo ngamba ni uburyo bwiza bwo kugabanya ibyago byo kwandura no gukumira ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Nubwo SARS-CoV-2 yaje nk'agakoko gashya mu bantu, kuba isa cyane na SARS-CoV nk'uko byatangajwe ku ya 7 Mutarama 2020, byari gutuma mu Bushinwa haba umutekano mwinshi ushingiye ku kwibuka cyane kwa SARS mu 2003.
Icyakora, kugeza ku itariki ya 19 Mutarama 2020, umuyobozi w'ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya indwara cya Wuhan ntiyahumurije abaturage avuga ko virusi nshya ifite ubwandu buke, ko ishobora gusaza umuntu ku wundi kandi ko nta kibazo cyo kwirinda no kugabanya ubwandu.
Ubu butumwa bwagabanyije cyane umutekano w'abaturage, cyane cyane mu gihe igihugu cyose cyari gitegura Umunsi Mukuru w'Imvura, kandi igihe cyari kigeze kugira ngo iki cyorezo kigere ku kigero gito muri Wuhan.
