Inkomoko y'inyamaswa za koronavirusi z'umuntu
Guhinduka no kumenyera byagiye bituma virusi za corona na za nyirayo, harimo n'abantu, zihinduka mu buryo buhuje n'imiterere mu gihe cy'imyaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi.
Mbere ya 2003, abantu bari bazi ko ubwoko bubiri bwa koronavirusi z'umuntu zitera indwara zidakomeye, urugero nk'ibicurane.
Icyorezo cya SARS na MERS cyatumye haboneka ikindi gice cy'ubwandu bwa HCoVs, cyerekana ko ishobora guteza akaga kandi ko ishobora guhitana ubuzima.
Igitero cya SARS-CoV-2 mu Bushinwa hagati mu mpera za 2019, cyongeye gushyira urumuri kuri koronavirusi, kandi byadutangaje kubona ikwirakwira vuba ariko ifite ubushobozi bwo gutera indwara ugereranyije na SARS-CoV.
Virusi ya HCoV ni indwara yaturutse mu nyamaswa, bityo gusobanukirwa inkomoko y'inyamaswa ya HCoVs bizadufasha cyane.
Virusi za corona nyinshi zituruka mu ducurama aho zitera indwara.
Hari n'abashumba b'abashoramari ba virusi ya HCoVs bamwe na bamwe bamenyekanye.
Kumenya inyamaswa z'inyamaswa bigira ingaruka zigaragara mu gukumira indwara z'abantu.
Gusuzuma imishyikirano hagati ya virusi ya corona n'umwakiriye mu nyamaswa, na byo bitanga ibisobanuro by'ingenzi ku birebana n'uko virusi ya corona ishobora kuba yarateye abantu.
Muri iyi nkuru, turatanga isesengura ry'amakuru ariho kuri koronavirusi ndwi z'umuntu, twibanda ku mateka yazo, inkomoko yazo mu nyamaswa no ku guhitana mu bwoko.
Icy'ingenzi ni uko tugereranya no guhanura virusi zitandukanye za coronavirus z'umuntu, tuzikurikiza uko virusi iterwa n'imiterere yayo n'uko genome zayo zisubirwamo.
Muri iyi nkuru, havugwa iby'indwara iterwa na koronavirusi (COVID-19) iriho ubu.
Byongeye kandi, byerekana ibyo guhindura umwirondoro bisaba kugira ngo umuntu agire icyo ageraho, n'ingaruka ziterwa no kwiyongera kw'imiterere y'iyo virusi ku burwayi.
Virusi za corona (coronavirus) ni zo mu muryango wa coronavirusi, zirimo urwego rw'ibicurane bya virusi bifite ADN imwe ifite uruzitiro rw'ibanze.
Izo virusi zifite genomini nini cyane kurusha izindi zose zifite ADN ya ribose, iri hagati ya 26 na 32 kB, kandi zitwa "coronaviruses" kubera ko zimeze nka corona iri munsi ya mikorosikopi.
Ku byerekeye imiterere y'ibinyabuzima, koronavirusi zifite genomes zitandukanyijwe zifite gahunda imwe.
Hafi bibiri bya gatatu by'imiterere y'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima bifite imiterere y'ibinyabuzima bibiri binini by'ibanze (ORF1a na ORF1b), bihindura ubwoko bwa pp1a na pp1ab.
Poroteyine nyinshi zirimo zirongera gukorerwa ibindi bikorwa kugira ngo ziterwe poroteyine 16 zitagira imiterere, zitwa nsp1~16.
Igice gisigaye cya genome gifite uburyo bwo gusoma bwa poroteyine z'ibanze, harimo spike S, E shell, membrane M na N.
Imiterere itandukanye ya koronavirusi kandi ihishira poroteyine nyinshi z'inyongera zaturutse mu bwoko bwihariye.
Hashingiwe ku itandukaniro ry'ibinyabuzima, virusi ya corona igabanyijemo ubwoko bune (virusi ya corona alpha, virusi ya corona beta, virusi ya corona gamma, na virusi ya corona delta), muri bwo hakaba harimo ubwoko bwa virusi ya corona beta, irimo virusi za corona nyinshi zo mu bantu, ikaba igabanyijemo ubwoko bune (A, B, C, W).
Ibimenyetso by'ihindagurika ry'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima byagaragaje ko udukoko n'imbeba ari byo bikomoka kuri virusi ya corona alpha na beta, mu gihe inyoni ari zo zikora cyane cyane virusi ya corona gamma na delta.
Mu gihe cy'imyaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi, koronavirusi yagiye isimburana n'izindi, zimwe muri zo zikaba zarateye indwara zikomeye mu bantu.
Kugeza ubu hamaze kumenyekana ubwoko burindwi bwa virusi ya corona.
Muri byo harimo virusi ya HCoV-229E na HCoV-NL63, ari na zo virusi za alpha.
Izindi virusi eshanu za beta zirimo virusi ya HCoV-OC43, virusi ya HKU1, SARS-CoV, SARS-CoV-2 na SARS-CoV-2.
Virusi ya HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, na HCoV-NL63 akenshi zitera ibimenyetso byoroheje, urugero nk'ibicurane cyangwa gucibwamwo cyangwa byombi.
Mu buryo bunyuranye, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 nshya zisanzwe zisanzwe zisanzwe ziterwa n'indwara nyinshi, zitera ubwandu bukomeye bw'ubuhumekero bwo hasi ku barwayi benshi cyane bafite ibyago byinshi byo kugira ikibazo cy'ubuhumekero bukabije (Acute Respiratory Syndrome) n'ibimenyetso bitari iby'ubuhumekero.
Coronavirus y'umuntu 229E, ubwoko bwa mbere B814, yavanywe mu byondo by'ibihaha by'abarwayi ba grippe mu myaka ya za 60.
Kuva icyo gihe, amakuru menshi yagiye akwirakwizwa binyuze mu bushakashatsi bwimbitse bwakozwe kuri virusi ya HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43, iyo virusi ikira ibimenyetso byayo.
Mu by'ukuri, abantu benshi bemeraga ko ubwandu bwa HCoVs butari bubi kugeza igihe habonekeye SARS.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2003 ni kimwe mu byorezo byishe abantu benshi cyane mu mateka yacu, aho abantu bagera ku 8.000 banduye iki cyorezo, naho abagera ku 10% bagakomereka.
Nyuma y'imyaka icumi, indwara ya MERS yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati, yari imaze igihe kirekire cyane mu karere ka Arabiya, ariko igakomeza gukwirakwira hirya no hino ku isi.
Virusi ya Corona 2019 (HCoV-2019), yahawe izina rya SARS-CoV-2, ni yo mpamvu y'icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), yahitanye abantu barenga 3,120 kandi ikandura abantu barenga 91,000 ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020.
Amatara aravuga, kandi isi igomba kwitegura icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2.
Virusi zose zirindwi za HCoVs zikomoka ku nyamaswa, zaba inyenzi cyangwa amatungo.
Hari ibimenyetso byinshi bishyigikira ko virusi za corona zose zaturutse mu nyamaswa zitwa udukoko, aho za virusi zisanzwe zisanzwe kandi zitera indwara, ariko zigaragaza itandukaniro rinini mu bigize ingirabuzima fatizo.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyateje ibibazo bikomeye mu buvuzi, mu bya siyansi, mu mibereho n'umuco mu Bushinwa no ku isi.
Gukurikirana inkomoko y'inyamaswa za HCoVs byagaragaje uburyo bwo gusobanukirwa amateka asanzwe, imbaraga zituma habaho n'ibintu bibuza abantu kujya mu bindi biremwa.
Ibi bishobora no kuyobora cyangwa koroshya ubushakashatsi ku byerekeye ikigega, ikigega cy'ubuvuzi n'inyamaswa z'ibanze (inyamaswa z'ibanze z'ibanze) za SARS-CoV-2, bigira ingaruka zikomeye mu gukumira ingaruka z'igihe kizaza.
Muri iyi nkuru, turatanga isesengura ry'inkomoko y'inyamaswa, ikwirakwira ry'ubwoko, n'indwara ziterwa na koronavirusi.
By'umwihariko, turashyira ahabona kandi tukaganira ku gitekerezo cyogeye ko virusi z'umwimerere za HCoVs zisanzwe zitera indwara mu bibanza byazo by'ibanze ariko zikaba zitera indwara nyuma yo kwimuka hagati y'ubwoko ku wundi muntu.
Nanone kandi, dusuzuma uko virusi ya HCoV yagiye ikora, aho ubwandu bwa virusi bwagendaga bwiyongera, akenshi bikagenda bigabanuka.
Muri iyi nkuru, turaganira ku ngaruka z'icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2.
Virusi za koronavirusi zo mu nyamaswa zamenyekanye mu mpera z'imyaka ya za 30.
Mbere y'uko ubwoko bwa B814 bwa HCoV-229E bufatwa bwa mbere mu byondo by'inzoka z'abarwayi ba grippe, hari ubwoko butandukanye bwa koronavirusi bwabaga bwaratoranyijwe mu nyamaswa zitandukanye zanduye, harimo inkoko, imbeba, inka, ingurube, imbwa n'injangwe.
