Abarwayi banduye virusi ya HCoV-229E bafite ibimenyetso bikunze kugaragara by'ibicurane, birimo umutwe, guhekenya, kugira ubumuga, kuribwa mu muhogo, kugira umuriro, no gukorora mu bice bigera ku 10 kugeza kuri 20%.
