Ibimenyetso bya HCoV-OC43 bisa n'aho ari kimwe n'ibitera HCoV-229E, idashobora gutandukanywa n'izindi virusi z'ubuhumekero nka virusi ya grippe A na virusi z'ibihaha.
Virusi ya HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43 byombi byarakwirakwiriye ku isi hose, kandi bikunze gukwirakwira mu gihe cy'imbeho mu bihe by'ubushyuhe.
Muri rusange, igihe cyo kubyara izo virusi kiba kitarenze icyumweru kimwe, hakurikirwa n'ibyumweru bibiri byo kumva urwaye.
Dukurikije ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'abantu bitangiye gukora, abantu bafite amagara mazima banduye virusi ya HCoV-229E, batangira kugira imbeho yoroheje.
Abarwayi bake cyane bafite uburwayi bwo mu rwego rw'ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri ni bo bagaragaje ko bahungabanye cyane mu buryo bw'ubuhumekero bwo hasi.
SARS, nanone izwi nka "Lunemia Luminosa", ni yo ndwara ya mbere ya coronavirus y'umuntu yanditswe neza mu mateka y'abantu, kandi ifite SARS-CoV-2 yo mu bwoko bwa SARS-CoV-2 ikaba ari virusi ya gatatu ya coronavirus y'umuntu yavumbuwe.
Umuntu wa mbere wahuye na SARS mu mpera z'umwaka wa 2002 mu ntara ya Guangdong mu Bushinwa.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyateje abantu 8,096 banduye, 774 bapfa, kandi cyakwirakwiriye mu bihugu byinshi no ku migabane myinshi.
Uretse umuntu utanga virusi, bivugwa ko umuntu umwe ashobora kwandura indwara ebyiri mu gihe cy'amasegonda abiri, mu gihe cy'iminsi 4 kugeza ku minsi 7, kandi virusi igenda iba nyinshi cyane ku munsi wa 10.
