Virusi yabonetse bwa mbere mu cyuma cy'umurwayi wa mbere wari mu muryango wavuye i Guangzhou ajya i Hong Kong.
Kuva icyo gihe, hashyizweho imihati ikomeye mu bushakashatsi ku cyorezo cya koronavirusi.
Virusi ya corona-NL63 y'umuntu yabonetse mu mwana w'amezi arindwi wo mu Buholandi mu mpera z'umwaka wa 2004.
Mu mizo ya mbere, byabonetse ko ari ibisanzwe mu bana bato, mu bantu bakuru, no mu barwayi bafite indwara z'ubuhumekero ziterwa n'uburwayi bw'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri.
Indwara z'ibicurane, gufatwa n'ibicurane, umuriro n'indwara y'ibicurane, ni ibimenyetso bikunze kugaragara by'indwara iterwa na virusi ya corona-NL63.
Ubundi bushakashatsi bwigenga bwagaragaje ko virusi imwe yavanywe mu cyuma cy'uruhanga cy'umwana w'amezi umunani ufite indwara y'ubuhumekero mu Buholandi.
Nubwo yavumbuwe mu Buholandi, yakwirakwiriye ku isi hose.
Bivugwa ko virusi ya HCoV-NL63 ari yo iteza hafi 4.7% by'indwara zisanzwe zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero, kandi ko iboneka cyane mu mpeshyi, mu mpeshyi no mu itumba.
Virusi ya corona-NL63 ifitanye isano n'indwara y'ubuhumekero, nanone izwi ku izina rya "chnush".
Muri uwo mwaka, virusi ya HKU1 y'umuntu yabonetse ku mugabo w'imyaka 71 wari warakomerekejwe n'indwara y'ibihaha na bronchitis muri Hong Kong.
Uretse indwara z'ibicurane n'indwara z'ibicurane, HKU1 yavuzwe ko ifitanye isano no kongera uburwayi bw'igituntu.
HKU1 yabonetse ko ikwirakwira ku isi hose, igateza indwara z'ubuhumekero zidakomeye, nk'iyi ya HKU-63, HKU-229E na HKU-OC43.
Iyi virusi ya HCoV 4 yavuye mu bantu, yose yisanze neza mu bantu, kandi muri rusange, nta bushobozi buhagije bwo guhinduka ngo itume habaho indwara zikwirakwira cyane. Ariko, byatewe n'impamvu zitazwi, nko mu gihe kitari cyoroshye cy'ubwoko bw'iyi virusi ya HCoV-NL63, iherutse kuvugwa ko iteza indwara nyinshi mu buhumekero bwo hasi mu Bushinwa.
