Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryavuze ko kongera ubushobozi no guhindura uburyo bw'ibigo nderabuzima kugira ngo bikemure ibibazo by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 ari ingenzi mu guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Ikigo cy'u Burayi gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (ECDC) n'ibiro by'akarere by'umuryango w'abibumbye byita ku buzima (OMS) byatanze amabwiriza ku bitaro n'imirimo y'ubuvuzi bw'ibanze yo kwimura umutungo ku byiciro byinshi, harimo gushyira imbaraga mu gupima COVID-19, guhagarika ibikorwa by'amahitamo aho bishoboka, gutandukanya no gutandukanya abantu banduye COVID-19, kongera ubushobozi bwo kwita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 binyuze mu gutoza abakozi no kongera umubare w'ibikoresho byo guhumeka no kwambara ibitanda.
Hariho ibitekerezo byinshi ku birebana n'aho ikibazo cya mbere cyatandukaniye (cyitwa Umurwayi wa Zero).
Umuntu wa mbere wamenyekanye ko yanduye coronavirus nshya ashobora kuba yarapfuye ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Mu gihe cy'ukwezi kumwe, umubare w'abanduye coronavirus muri Hubei wariyongereye cyane.
Ibi ahanini byari bifitanye isano n'isoko rya Wuhan ry'ibiribwa by'ibinyamushongo, na ryo rigurisha inyamaswa nzima. Imwe mu mitekerereze ivuga ko virusi yavuye mu bwoko bw'inyamaswa; cyangwa se mu yandi magambo, ko ikomoka ku nyamaswa.
Ku ya 30 Ukuboza, itsinda ry'abaganga bo mu bitaro bya Wuhan Central ryahaye bagenzi babo umuburo ku "virusi ya SARS-like coronavirus".
Abaganga umunani muri bo, barimo Lee Wen Liang, bari barahawe igihano na polisi kubera ko bakwirakwije ibihuha, undi muganga witwa Ai Wen, yahawe igihano n'abakuru be cyo gukangurira abantu.
Nyuma yaho, Komisiyo y'Ubuzima y'Akarere ka Wuhan yasohoye itangazo ku mugaragaro ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza, kandi ibwira Umuryango w'Abibumbye wita ku Buzima (OMS).
Abategetsi b'ubuzima muri Wuhan babonye umubare uhagije w'abantu banduye indwara y'ibicurane by'ibihaha bitazwi, bituma batangira gukora iperereza mu ntangiriro za Mutarama. Mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya mbere, umubare w'abantu banduye wari wikubye kabiri buri minsi irindwi n'igice.
Mu ntangiriro no hagati muri Mutarama 2020, virusi yageze mu zindi ntara z'Ubushinwa, ifashwa n'ingendo zo mu gihe cy'Umwaka Mushya w'Ubushinwa, ndetse na Kun, Wuhan, ikigo cy'ingendo n'aho imihanda minini ya gari ya moshi ihurira.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, Ubushinwa bwatangaje abantu bashya bagera kuri 140 mu munsi umwe, barimo babiri mu mujyi wa Beijing n'umwe mu mujyi wa Shenzhen.
Amakuru yemewe nyuma agaragaza ko abantu 6,174 bamaze kugaragaza ibimenyetso ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama 2020. Ku ya 26 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zarenze u Bushinwa n'u Butaliyani ku mubare munini w'abamaze kwandura ku isi. Ku ya 9 Mata 2020, amakuru yagaragaje ko ku isi hose hari abantu barenga miliyoni 1.61 bamaze kwandura, aho abantu barenga 97,000 bapfuye, abandi barenga 364,000 bagakira.
Ibihugu bigera kuri 200 n'uturere twaho byiboneye nibura umuntu umwe.
Kubera icyorezo cyugarije u Burayi, ibihugu byinshi byo mu karere ka Schengen byagabanyije ubwisanzure bwo kugenda no gushyiraho amabwiriza yo kugenzura imipaka.
Ibisubizo by'igihugu byashyizwemo ingamba zo kwirinda, nko kuguma mu rugo (byitwa amabwiriza yo kuguma mu rugo, amabwiriza yo kwirinda ahantu, cyangwa gufunga) no gufunga ingendo. Kuva ku ya 2 Mata, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 300 cyangwa 90% by'abaturage, bari mu bihe by'amabwiriza yo gufunga muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, abantu barenga miliyoni 50 bari mu bihe by'amabwiriza yo gufunga muri Filipine, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 59 bari mu bihe by'amabwiriza yo gufunga muri Afurika y'Epfo, abantu bagera kuri miliyari 1.3 bari mu bihe by'amabwiriza yo gufunga mu Buhinde.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe, abantu miliyari 1.7 ku isi hose bari mu buryo runaka bwo gufunga, umubare wariyongereye ugera kuri miliyari 2.6 nyuma y'iminsi ibiri, hafi kimwe cya gatatu cy'abatuye isi.
Umuntu wa mbere wemejwe ko arwaye COVID-19 yavutse ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 i Wuhan; raporo imwe itari yemewe ivuga ko umuntu wa mbere yanduye ari ku itariki ya 17 Ugushyingo.
Dr Zhang Jixian yabonye icyorezo cy'indwara y'ibicurane ku itariki ya 26 Ukuboza, maze ibitaro bye bibimenyesha ikigo gishinzwe kugenzura indwara cya Jianghan Buhan ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza.
Igenzura ry'ibanze ry'imiterere y'abarwayi ryabaye ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza 2019 ryagaragaje ko hari virusi ya SARS.
Komisiyo y'ubuzima ya Wuhan yasohoye itangazo rusange ku wa 31 Ukuboza.
Umunsi umwe, WHO yabimenyeshejwe.
Mu gihe habagaho izi mbwirwaruhame, abapolisi baburiye abaganga bo muri Wuhan ku "kuvuga ibihuha" by'icyorezo.
Komisiyo y'igihugu y'ubuzima mu Bushinwa yabanje kuvuga ko nta "gihamya gifatika" cy'uko umuntu ashobora kwandura undi.
Mu mpera za Mutarama, leta y'Ubushinwa yatangije gahunda ikomeye cyane, nyuma yaho Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Ishyaka ry'Abakomunisiti ry'Ubushinwa Xi Jinping yayise "intambara y'abaturage" yo gukumira ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Mu byiswe "guhagarika abantu benshi mu mateka y'abantu", itegeko ryo guhagarika ingendo z'abantu benshi zaturutse i Wuhan ryatangajwe ku ya 23 Mutarama, rigera mu mijyi 15 yo mu mujyi wa Hubei, rigira ingaruka ku bantu bagera kuri miliyoni 57.
Gukoresha imodoka bwite muri uyu mujyi birabujijwe.
Ibirori byo kwizihiza Umwaka Mushya w'Abashinwa (itariki 25 Mutarama) byahagaritswe mu duce twinshi.
Abayobozi batangaje kandi ko bagiye kubaka ibitaro by'agateganyo, ibitaro bya Huoshen Shan, byuzuye mu minsi 10.
Nyuma yaho, hubatswe ikindi bitaro, icyitwa Lichenshan, kugira ngo gikemure abarwayi benshi.
Usibye ibitaro bishya byashyizweho, Ubushinwa bwahinduye ibindi bigo 14 i Wuhan, nk'ibigo by'amakoraniro n'ibibuga by'imikino, mu bitaro by'agateganyo. Ku ya 26 Mutarama, leta yafashe izindi ngamba zo guhashya icyorezo cya COVID-19, harimo gutanga amatangazo y'ubuzima ku bantu batemberezaga no kongera iminsi mikuru y'ihinga.
Kaminuza n'amashuri na byo byafunzwe mu gihugu hose.
Hong Kong na Macau byashyizeho ingamba zitandukanye, cyane cyane ku mashuri na za kaminuza.
Ingamba zo gukora kure zafashwe mu turere twinshi two mu Bushinwa.
Imyigaragambyo yo mu mujyi wa Hobby no hanze yayo yarabujijwe.
Imodoka za Leta zavuguruwe, kandi amazu ndangamurage yafunzwe by'agateganyo mu Bushinwa hose.
Mu mijyi myinshi, abantu bagera kuri miriyoni 760 (abarenga kimwe cya kabiri cy'abaturage) bari mu nzira z'urugendo. Nyuma y'uko iki cyorezo cyakwiriye isi yose muri Werurwe, abategetsi b'Ubushinwa bafashe ingamba zikomeye zo kwirinda ko virusi "yinjira" mu gihugu ivuye mu bindi bihugu.
Urugero, Beijing yashyizeho iminsi 14 yo kwigunga ku bantu bose bagaruka mu mujyi baturutse mu bindi bihugu. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, hari umuntu umwe wanduye mu gihugu cye mu minsi itanu ishize, mu gihugu cy'u Bushinwa, binyuze mu muntu wari uturutse i Istanbul, agana i Guangzhou.
Ku ya 24 Werurwe 2020, Perezida w'Inama y'Igihugu y'Ubushinwa, Li Ke Chiang, yavuze ko umubare w'abandura mu gihugu cyabo wagabanutse kandi ko icyorezo cyagabanutse mu Bushinwa.
Imipaka ku rugendo muri Hubei yarorohejwe kuri uwo munsi, usibye Wuhan, nyuma y'amezi abiri ya Guma mu Rugo. Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'u Bushinwa yatangaje ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020 ko abafite viza cyangwa ibyangombwa byo kuba mu gihugu bahagaritswe guhera ku ya 28 Werurwe, ariko nta makuru arambuye yerekeranye n'igihe iyo politiki izarangirira.
Abashaka kwinjira mu Bushinwa bagomba gusaba viza muri ambasade cyangwa muri konsula y'Ubushinwa.
Guverinoma y'Ubushinwa yasabye inganda no inganda gutangira imirimo ku ya 30 Werurwe, kandi itanga inkunga y'amafaranga ku nganda. Inama ya Leta yatangaje umunsi wo kuboroga utangira ku ya 4 Mata saa kumi n'ebyiri, mu gihe cya Qingming Festival, nubwo guverinoma y'igihugu yasabye imiryango kugaragariza icyubahiro binyuze kuri interineti mu kwirinda kongera gukwirakwira kwa COVID-19.
COVID-19 yemejwe ko yageze muri Koreya y'Epfo ivuye mu Bushinwa ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama 2020.
Ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe ubuzima cyatangaje ko umubare w'abanduye wiyongereye cyane ku itariki ya 20 Gashyantare, bikaba byatewe ahanini n'uko mu mujyi wa Daegu habaye itsinda rishya ry'idini ryitwa Shincheonji Jesus Church.
Abantu b'i Shenzhen basuye Daegu baturutse i Wuhan bakekwaho kuba ari bo batumye iki cyorezo kivuka.
Kuva ku ya 22 Gashyantare, abantu 1,261 cyangwa hafi 13% by'abayoboke 9,336 ba Kiliziya bari bafite ibimenyetso. Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje ko ifite umutekano ku rwego rwo hejuru ku ya 23 Gashyantare 2020.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abantu barenga 2,000 bemejwe ko banduye muri Koreya, aho ku ya 29 Gashyantare bari bageze ku 3150.
Ibigo bya gisirikare byose byo muri Koreya y'Epfo byashyizwe mu kato nyuma y'uko abasirikare batatu bavuye mu bigeragezo byemejwe ko banduye virusi.
Ibihe by'indege na byo byarafashwe, hanyuma bihinduka. Koreya y'Epfo yashyizeho gahunda yafashwe nk'iyikomeye kandi iteganyijwe neza kurusha izindi ku isi yo gupima abantu bakareba niba bafite virusi, no gutandukanya abanduye, no gukurikirana ababasanganye no kubavana mu ngo zabo.
Uburyo bwo gupima harimo gutanga amakuru ku bimenyetso by'abantu bashya baturutse mu mahanga bakoresheje porogaramu ya telefoni, gupima abantu mu modoka zabo ku munsi ukurikiyeho, no kongera ubushobozi bwo gupima abantu bagera ku 20,000 ku munsi.
Porogaramu ya Koreya y'Epfo yerekana ko yatsinze icyorezo nubwo nta mijyi yose yashyizweho mu kato. Mu mizo ya mbere, abaturage ba Koreya y'Epfo bari bagabanye ku buryo Perezida Moon Jae-in yabyitwayemo.
Abanyakoreya benshi basinye impapuro zisaba ko Moon yafungwa, bavuga ko leta yafashe nabi icyorezo, cyangwa se ko yashimye uburyo yabyitwayemo.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko Koreya y'Epfo yari ifite umubare muto w'abanduye umunsi umwe mu byumweru bine.
Ku itariki ya 29 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko guhera ku itariki ya 1 Mata, abantu bose bashya bazava mu mahanga bazajya bashyirwa mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Nk'uko amakuru yo ku wa 1 Mata abivuga, Koreya y'Epfo yakiriye ubusabe bw'ibihugu 121 bitandukanye byo gufasha mu gupima virusi.
Irani yatangaje ku nshuro ya mbere icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 cyemejwe ku ya 19 Gashyantare mu mujyi wa Qum, aho abantu babiri bapfuye nyuma y'aho kuri uwo munsi, nk'uko Minisiteri y'Ubuzima n'Uburezi bw'Ubuvuzi yabitangaje.
Ingamba za mbere zatangajwe na leta harimo guhagarika ibitaramo, indi mihango y'umuco n'imikino, amasengesho yo ku wa Gatanu, gufunga kaminuza, amashuri makuru n'amashuri.
Irani yashyizeho miliyari eshanu za riyal mu kurwanya virusi.
Perezida Hassan Rouhani yatangaje ku ya 26 Gashyantare 2020 ko nta gahunda yo gufunga uturere twibasiwe n'iki cyorezo, ko abantu bonyine bazajya bafatwa.
Imyiteguro yo kugabanya ingendo hagati y'imijyi yatangaje muri Werurwe, nubwo imodoka nyinshi zakomeje kugendana hagati y'imijyi mbere y'umwaka mushya w'Abaperesi witwa Nuruz.
Ahantu hahurira abayoboke ba Shia mu Gukuraho hagumye hagaragara kugeza ku ya 16 Werurwe 2020. Muri Gashyantare, Irani yabaye ikigo cya mbere cy'icyorezo nyuma y'u Bushinwa.
Hagati y'ibirego by'uko Irani ihishe icyorezo, ibihugu birenga icumi byakurikiranye abarwayi bavuye muri Irani guhera ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare, bivuga ko icyorezo gishobora kurenga 388 leta ya Irani yatangaje kugeza kuri iyo tariki.
Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Irani yafunzwe, aho abanyamuryango 23 muri 290 bari bayigize bagaragaye ko banduye virusi ya Corona tariki ya 3 Werurwe.
Ku ya 12 Werurwe, umuryango uharanira uburenganzira bwa muntu Human Rights Watch wasabye abayobozi ba gereza za Irani kurekura by'agateganyo abarwanashyaka bazira guhakana amahoro, no kurekura by'agateganyo imfungwa zifite uburenganzira.
Yavuze ko hari akaga gakomeye ko kwandura virusi mu bibanza by'imfungwa, aho kandi nta buvuzi buhagije buhari.
Ku ya 15 Werurwe, leta ya Irani yatangaje ko abantu 100 bapfuye mu munsi umwe, umubare munini w'abantu bapfuye mu gihugu kuva icyorezo cyatangira.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 17 Werurwe, nibura abanyapolitiki 12 n'abari abayobozi ba leta bapfuye bazize iyo ndwara.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, Irani yari imaze kubona abantu bashya 50 banduye buri saha, n'umuntu umwe upfa buri minota 10 kubera coronavirus.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'umukozi wa OMS, umubare w'abandura muri Irani ushobora kuba wikubye inshuro eshanu.
Hari n'abandi batekereza ko ibihano bya Amerika kuri Irani bishobora kugira ingaruka ku bushobozi bw'igihugu mu by'imari bwo guhangana n'icyorezo.
Komisiyo y'Umuryango w'Abibumbye y'Uburenganzira bwa Muntu yasabye ko ibihano by'ubukungu bigabanywa ku bihugu byazahajwe cyane n'iki cyorezo, harimo na Irani.
Icyorezo cyemejwe mu Butaliyani ku ya 31 Mutarama, ubwo abakerarugendo b'Abashinwa bari i Roma bageragereshwaga SARS-CoV-2.
Abarwayi batangiye kwiyongera cyane, bituma leta y'Ubutaliyani ihagarika ingendo zose z'indege zituruka mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bihugu, ndetse itangaza ko ari mu bihe by'ubukungu bwihuse.
Nyuma yaho, habonetse abantu batandukanye banduye COVID-19, batangira ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare mu ntara ya Lombardy. Ku itariki ya 22 Gashyantare, inama y'abaminisitiri yatangaje itegeko rishya ryo gukumira iki cyorezo, harimo no gushyira abantu barenga 50,000 mu kato mu mirenge 11 itandukanye yo mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani.
Minisitiri w'intebe Giuseppe Conte yagize ati "Nta muntu uzemererwa kwinjira cyangwa gusohoka mu turere tw'icyorezo.
Mu by'ukuri, imirimo n'imikino byarahagaritswe muri utwo turere". Ku itariki ya 4 Werurwe, leta y'u Butaliyani yategetse ko amashuri yose na za kaminuza bifungwa burundu mu gihugu hose, aho mu Butaliyani hapfuye abantu 100.
Imikino yose ikomeye, harimo n'imikino ya shampiyona y'icyiciro cya mbere, yagombaga kubera mu nzu z'abakinnyi kugeza muri Mata, ariko ku itariki ya 9 Werurwe, imikino yose yahagaritswe by'agateganyo mu gihe cy'ukwezi kumwe.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Inte yategetse guhagarika ibikorwa byose byubucuruzi, usibye amaduka manini n'amavuriro. Ku ya 6 Werurwe, Ishuri ry'Ubutaliyani ry'ubutabire, ubutabazi, gusana no kwita ku barwayi (SIAARTI) ryasohoye inama z'imibanire y'abaganga ku bijyanye na protokoli zo gutandukanya zishobora gukoreshwa.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe, Ubutaliyani bwatsinze Ubushinwa nk'igihugu cyagize umubare munini w'abapfuye bazira coronavirus ku isi nyuma yo gutanga amakuru y'abantu 3,405 bishwe n'iki cyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 22 Werurwe, Uburusiya bwohereje mu Butaliyani indege icyenda z'ingabo zitwaye ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi.
Kugeza ku ya 5 Mata, abamaze kwandura bari 128,948, abamaze gupfa bari 15,887, kandi abamaze kwandura bari 21,815 mu Butaliyani, abenshi muri bo bakaba bari mu karere ka Lombardy.
Raporo ya CNN igaragaza ko umubare munini w'abantu bakuze n'ubushobozi bwo gupima abantu bose banduye virusi kugeza ubu mu Butaliyani bishobora kuba byaratumye umubare w'abapfa wiyongera.
Igisubizo cy'u Bwongereza kuri virusi cyagaragaye bwa mbere ko ari cyo cyoroshye kurusha ibindi bihugu byibasiwe n'iyo ndwara, kandi kugeza ku itariki ya 18 Werurwe 2020, leta y'u Bwongereza ntiyigeze ishyiraho uburyo ubwo ari bwo bwose bwo kwirinda abantu cyangwa gushyira abaturage mu kato.
Ingaruka zabaye iz'uko leta yanenzwe kubera kubura umuvuduko n'ubushishozi mu gusubiza impungenge abaturage bafite. Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Boris Johnson yasohoye itangazo rigira inama yo kwirinda ingendo cyangwa imikoranire itari ngombwa, agasaba abantu gukora kuva mu rugo uko bishoboka kose no kwirinda ahantu hatandukanye, nko mu tubari, mu biryo no mu bitaramo.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, guverinoma yatangaje ko izafunga ibigo byose by'imyidagaduro nka za pub na za gym vuba bishoboka, kandi yasezeranyije ko izishyura abakozi bagera kuri 80% by'umushahara w'abakozi ku mafaranga y'u Bwongereza 2.500 ku kwezi mu rwego rwo kugabanya ubushomeri mu gihe cy'ibibazo. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe yatangaje ingamba zikomeye zo gutandukanya abantu, aho amateraniro y'abantu barenga babiri yabuzanyijwe kandi ingendo no gukora imirimo hanze y'urugo byarabuzanyijwe keretse ari ngombwa cyane.
Mu buryo bunyuranye n'ingamba zabanje, izi mbogamizi zashyizweho n'abapolisi binyuze mu gutanga amande no gutatanya abantu.
Amategeko yo gufunga inganda nyinshi, uretse ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi "by'ingenzi", harimo amaduka manini, ibicuruzwa, amabanki, amaduka acuruza ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga, sitasiyo za lisansi, n'amagaraji.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, umuntu wa mbere wamenyekanye ko arwaye COVID-19 muri leta ya Washington mu majyaruguru ashyira uburengerazuba bw'inyanja ya Pacific, yasubiye iwabo avuye i Wuhan ku ya 15 Mutarama.
Itsinda ry'ibiro by'umukuru w'igihugu ryashyizweho ku itariki ya 29 Mutarama.
Ku ya 31 Mutarama, ubuyobozi bwa Trump bwatangaje ko habonetse ikibazo cy'ubukungu bw'abaturage, kandi bushyiraho imipaka ku kwinjira kw'abagenzi baturutse mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020, ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kugenzura indwara (CDC), cyatangaje ko cyateguye uburyo bwacyo bwo gupima.
Nubwo Amerika yakoze ibyo, yatinze gutangiza igerageza, bituma hatamenyekana neza uko icyo cyorezo cyari giteye icyo gihe.
Iki kizamini cyasenye ikizamini cyabitswe na leta muri Gashyantare, kubura kwemerwa na leta ku byiciro by'ibizamini bitari ibya leta (bikorwa n'amashuri, ibigo by'ubucuruzi n'ibitaro) kugeza mu mpera za Gashyantare, n'ibipimo by'abantu by'uko bakwiriye guhabwa iki kizamini kugeza mu ntangiriro za Werurwe (bitumaga hakenerwa itegeko rya muganga).
Kugeza ku ya 27 Gashyantare, Washington Post yatangaje ko muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika hakorwa ibizamini bitarenga 4,000.
Ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe, ikinyamakuru The Atlantic cyavuze ko hatangijwe ibizamini bitarenga 14.000.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, Associated Press yatangaje iti "Abantu benshi bafite ibimenyetso kandi bafite amabwiriza ya muganga bategereje amasaha cyangwa iminsi yo gupimwa". Nyuma yo gutangaza icyorezo cya mbere muri Amerika muri leta ya Washington ku ya 29 Gashyantare, Guverineri Jay Insley yatangaje ko ari mu bihe by'ubukungu, igikorwa cyagiye gikurikirwa n'ibindi bihugu.
Amashuri yo mu mujyi wa Seattle yahagaritse amasomo ku ya 3 Werurwe, kandi mu kwezi kwa gatatu hagati, amashuri yose yafunzwe mu gihugu. Ku ya 6 Werurwe 2020, Amerika yamenyeshejwe ibijyanye n'ingaruka z'icyorezo cya coronavirus gishya ku gihugu n'abahanga mu by'indwara z'ibyorezo bo muri kaminuza ya Imperial College London.
Kuri uwo munsi, Perezida Trump yashyize umukono ku itegeko ryo gutanga inkunga yo kwitegura no gusubiza coronavirus, ryatanze inkunga y'ibigo bya leta ya miliyari 8.3 z'amadolari yo guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Amashyirahamwe yashyizeho imipaka ku ngendo z'abakozi, yahagaritse inama, kandi asaba abakozi gukora bari mu rugo.
Ibikorwa n'imikino byarahagaritswe. Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Trump yatangaje ko ingendo mu bice byinshi by'u Burayi, uretse mu Bwongereza, zizaba zihagaritswe mu gihe cy'iminsi 30, guhera ku ya 13 Werurwe.
Ku munsi wakurikiyeho, ingamba z'uko igihugu cyabo cyajya mu Bwongereza no muri Irilande zarushijeho kwiyongera.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe, yatangaje ko igihugu gifite ikibazo cy'ubukungu, cyemerera gukoresha amafaranga ya leta mu guhangana n'ikibazo.
Guhera ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe, ibigo byinshi byarafunze cyangwa bigabanyiriza amasaha y'akazi muri Amerika yose mu rwego rwo kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Ku ya 17 Werurwe, icyorezo cyemejwe mu bihugu byose 50 no mu Karere ka Columbia. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, abantu 10,700 banduye Coronavirus mu mujyi wa New York, barenga umubare w'abanduye muri Koreya y'Epfo.
Ku ya 25 Werurwe, guverineri yavuze ko guhagarika abantu kugaragara ko byagize icyo bigeraho, aho imibare igaragaza ko umubare w'abandura wiyongereyeho kabiri, uva ku minsi 2.0 ugera ku minsi 4.7.
Kugeza ku ya 28 Werurwe, hari abantu 32,308 bamaze kwandura muri New York City, abantu 672 bakaba barapfuye bazize virusi. Ku ya 26 Werurwe, muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika hemejwe ko hari abantu benshi banduye coronavirus kurusha mu kindi gihugu icyo ari cyo cyose ku isi, harimo Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani.
Nk'uko itangazamakuru ryabitangaje ku ya 30 Werurwe, Perezida wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Trump, yafashe icyemezo cyo kongera amabwiriza yo kwirinda abantu kugeza ku ya 30 Mata.
Kuri uwo munsi, ubwato bw'ibitaro bwitwa USS Comfort, bwari bufite ibitanda bigera ku 1.000, bwashyize ikirindiro mu mujyi wa New York.
Ku ya 3 Mata, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zagize abantu 884 bapfuye bazize coronavirus mu masaha 24.
Muri leta ya New York, umubare w'abanduye warenze 100,000 ku ya 3 Mata. White House yanenzwe kubera ko itesha agaciro ibyago no kugenzura amakuru binyuze mu kuyobora abayobozi b'ubuzima n'abahanga mu bya siyansi guhuza amakuru rusange n'ibitabo by'ibyavugiwe kuri virusi n'ibiro bya Visi Perezida Mike Pence.
Ubuyobozi bwa Trump kuri iki kibazo ntibwakiriwe neza kuko bwatumye habaho amakimbirane mu nzego zitandukanye.
Bamwe mu bayobozi n'abatanga ibitekerezo b'Abanyamerika banenze ko Amerika ikomeza kwinjiza ibintu by'ibanze, harimo n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi by'ibanze, mu Bushinwa.
Isesengura ry'ingendo zo mu kirere ryakoreshejwe mu gushushanya no guhanura uburyo bwo gukwirakwira, byasohotse mu kinyamakuru cyitwa Travel Medicine mu kwezi kwa mbere 2020.
Hashingiwe ku makuru yo mu mwaka wa 2018 yatanzwe n'ishyirahamwe mpuzamahanga ry'indege, Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo na Taipei ni byo bihugu byafashe abagenzi benshi cyane baturutse i Wuhan.
Dubai, Sydney na Melbourne na byo byavuzwe ko ari ahantu hakunzwe cyane n'abagenzi baturutse i Wuhan.
Bali yavuzwe ko ari yo ifite ubushobozi buke mu byerekezo 20 bikunzwe cyane mu bijyanye no kwitegura, mu gihe imijyi yo muri Ositaraliya yabonetse ko ifite ubushobozi bwinshi. Australia yasohoye gahunda yayo yo guhangana n'iki cyorezo cya COVID-19 ku ya 7 Gashyantare.
Yavuze ko nta byinshi byamenyekanye kuri COVID-19, kandi ko Australia igiye kongera ingufu mu kugenzura imipaka n'itumanaho mu guhangana n'icyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 21 Werurwe, muri Ositaraliya hashyizweho ikibazo cy'umutekano w'ibinyabuzima.
Kubera ko ingendo rusange z'abantu zitewe n'uburyo bwo kwirinda mu mujyi wa Wuhan na Hubei, ibihugu byinshi byateguye gukura abaturage babyo n'abakozi ba dipolomasi muri ako karere, cyane cyane binyuze mu ndege z'indege z'igihugu cyabo, mu gihe abategetsi b'Ubushinwa batanga ibyangombwa.
Kanada, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, Ubuyapani, u Buhinde, Sri Lanka, Ositaraliya, u Bufaransa, Arijantine, u Budage na Tayilande, ni bimwe mu bihugu byabanje gutegura ko abaturage babyo bakurwa mu byabo.
Pakisitani yatangaje ko itazongera kohereza abaturage bayo mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 7 Gashyantare, Brezili yakuye muri icyo gihugu Abanyakoreziya 34 cyangwa abantu bari bafashwe, hamwe n'Abanyapolonye bane, Umushinwa n'Umuhindi.
Abaturage b'Abanyapolonye, Abashinwa n'Abahindi bavuye mu ndege muri Polonye, aho indege ya Brezili yahagaritse mbere yo gutangira urugendo rwayo yerekeza muri Brezili.
Abaturage ba Brazil bagiye i Wuhan bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cya gisirikare kiri hafi ya Brasilia.
Kuri uwo munsi, Abakanada 215 (176 bavuye mu ndege ya mbere, 39 bavuye mu ndege ya kabiri yari yaraguzwe na Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika) bakuwe i Wuhan bajyanwa mu kigo cya gisirikare cya Canada Trenton kubacumbikira mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare, indi ndege yari itwaye Abakanada 185 ivuye i Wuhan, yaguye ku kigo cya gisirikare cya Canada cya Trenton.
Abategetsi ba Ositaraliya bavanye abaturage 277 ku itariki ya 3 n'iya 4 Gashyantare, babajyana mu kigo cyo ku kirwa cya Noheli, cyongeye gukoreshwa nk'ikigo cyo gushyira abantu mu kato, aho bamaze iminsi 14.
Indege yo guhungisha abantu yo muri Nouvelle-Zélande yageze muri Auckland ku ya 5 Gashyantare, kandi abagenzi bayo (harimo n'abantu baturutse muri Australia na Pasifika) bari mu kato ku kigo cy'abasirikare mu mazi i Whangaparawa mu majyaruguru ya Auckland.
Ku itariki ya 15 Gashyantare, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika zatangaje ko zizakura Abanyamerika bari mu bwato bw'ubwato bw'ubwato bwitwa Diamond Princess.
Ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, indege yari itwaye abantu 129 bo muri Kanada bari bavuye mu bwato bwitwaga Diamond Princess, yaguye i Trenton, mu ntara ya Ontario.
Mu ntangiriro z'ukwezi kwa Werurwe, leta y'Ubuhinde yatangiye gukura abaturage bayo muri Irani. Ku itariki ya 14 Werurwe, indege ya South African Airways yari yarakodeshejwe na leta y'Afurika y'Epfo yasubije abaturage 112 bo muri Afurika y'Epfo.
Aba bana ba mbere bo muri Afurika y'Epfo bagaragaye ibimenyetso bya coronavirus baremerewe kujya mu bitaro kugira ngo bigabanya ibyago byo kwandura.
Abanyafurika y'Epfo bageragejwe gusa bageragejwe nabi.
Ibyavuye mu igerageza byerekanye ko Abanyafurika y'Epfo, barimo abakozi bo mu ndege, abaterageti, abakozi bo muri hoteli, abapolisi n'abasirikare bitabiriye igikorwa cy'ubutabazi, bose bagumye mu kato n'uburinzi mu biruhuko bya Ranch mu gihe cy'iminsi 14, nta ndwara bakomeretse.
Ku itariki ya 20 Werurwe, Amerika yatangiye gukura ingabo zayo muri Iraki kubera icyorezo.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'u Bushinwa yatangaje ko ibihugu 21 (harimo Belarusi, Pakistan, Trinité, Tobago, Misiri na Irani) byohereje imfashanyo mu Bushinwa.
Bamwe mu banyeshuri b'Abashinwa bo muri kaminuza zo muri Amerika bafatanyije mu kohereza imfashanyo mu bice by'u Bushinwa byugarijwe na virusi. Itsinda ry'abakozi bo mu karere ka Chicago ryatangaje ko ryabashije kohereza udupfukamunwa 50,000 tw'abantu bafite ubumuga bwa N95 mu bitaro byo mu ntara ya Hubei ku itariki ya 30 Mutarama.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batangaje ko batanze miliyoni 100 z'amadolari y'Amerika mu rwego rwo gushyigikira ubushakashatsi ku nkingo no kuvura, ndetse no kurinda "abaturage bafite ibyago muri Afurika no muri Aziya y'Amajyepfo".
Interaction yatangaje ko guverinoma y'Ubushinwa yatanze udupfukamunwa 200,000 ku wa 6 Gashyantare, nyuma y'aho Senateri Richard Gordon yohereje udupfukamunwa miliyoni 3.16 i Wuhan.
Ku ya 19 Gashyantare, Croix Rouge y'i Singapore yatangaje ko igiye kohereza inkunga ya miliyoni 2.26 z'amadolari mu Bushinwa.
Ubuyapani bwatanze udupfukamunwa miliyoni imwe, Turukiya yohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, Uburusiya bwohereje toni zirenga 13 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi i Wuhan, Maleziya yatangaje ko yatanze imyenda y'impu 18 miliyoni mu Bushinwa, Ubudage bwatanze ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi birimo imyenda 10,000 yo kurinda, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatanze toni 17.8 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa, kandi zitanga indi miliyoni 100 z'amadolari yo gufasha ibihugu byibasiwe n'icyorezo. Nyuma y'uko ibibazo byamaze kugaruka mu Bushinwa, leta yohereje imfashanyo mu bihugu bitandukanye byibasiwe n'icyorezo.
Muri Werurwe, Ubushinwa, Cuba n'Uburusiya byohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'impuguke zo gufasha Ubutaliyani guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Umucuruzi Jack Ma yohereje i Addis Ababa muri Ethiopia, imigabane ya miliyoni 1.1 yo gupima, miliyoni 6 z'udupfukamunwa n'imyenda 60,000 yo kurinda umubiri, aho AU yagabanyije.
Nyuma yo kohereza muri Panama, yohereje ibikoresho 5,000 byo gupima, udupfukamunwa 100,000 n'ibikoresho bitanu byo guhumeka.
MAH yanahaye Canada ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi. U Buholandi, Esipanye, Turukiya, Jeworujiya na Repubulika ya Tchèque byagaragaje impungenge ku byumba byo gupima n'ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga byakozwe mu Bushinwa.
Urugero, Espagne yakuye ibikoresho 58 000 byo gupima virusi ya corona byakozwe mu Bushinwa, byari bifite ubushobozi bwo gupima 30% gusa, mu gihe mu Buholandi hari hamaze gusubizwa 600,000 by'udupfukamunwa twakozwe mu Bushinwa twari dufite inenge.
Ububiligi bwasubije 100,000 by'udupfukamunwa tutakoreshwa twatekerezaga ko twavuye mu Bushinwa, ariko mu by'ukuri twavuye muri Kolombiya.
Ku rundi ruhande, ibice bya Amerika y'Epfo na Afurika byishimiye inkunga y'Ubushinwa. Ku itariki ya 2 Mata, Banki y'Isi yatangije ibikorwa by'ubutabazi mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere.
OMS yashimye cyane abayobozi b'Ubushinwa ku mihati bashyizeho mu gucunga no gukumira iki cyorezo.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryabonye itandukaniro hagati y'icyorezo cya SARS cyabaye mu 2002 na 2004, aho abayobozi b'Ubushinwa bashinjwaga ko bari mu bihe by'umwijima byatumaga hatagira uburyo bwo kwirinda no kugabanya ubwandu, n'ikibazo kiriho ubu, aho leta y'u Bushinwa yatanze "amakuru buri gihe yo kwirinda ubwoba mbere y'iminsi mikuru y'umwaka mushya w'ubunani".
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, mu gusubiza icyemezo cy'ubuyobozi bw'ibanze cyo gushyiraho gahunda yo gufunga imodoka muri Wuhan, uhagarariye WHO, Gooden Gallia, yavuze ko nubwo "nta gushidikanya ko atari inama yatanzwe na WHO", ariko ko ari "ikimenyetso gikomeye cyo kubahiriza icyorezo aho cyibasiwe cyane", avuga ko ari "ikitigeze kibaho mu mateka y'ubuzima rusange". Ku ya 30 Mutarama, nyuma yo kwemeza ko umuntu umwe yavuye mu wundi hanze y'Ubushinwa, kandi umubare w'abandura mu bindi bihugu na wo wiyongera, WHO yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ubutabazi bw'ubuzima rusange (PHEIC), kikaba ari icyiciro cya gatandatu cy'ibibazo by'ubuzima rusange ku isi kuva iki cyorezo cyatangira gukorerwa mu mwaka wa 2009.
Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS yavuze ko icyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ubutabazi ku isi hose kubera "akaga ko gukwirakwira ku isi hose, cyane cyane mu bihugu bifite amafaranga make n'agati mu gihugu bidafite uburyo bwiza bwo kwita ku buzima.
Mu gusubiza ku bijyanye no gushyiraho ingamba zo kugabanya ingendo, Tedros yavuze ko "nta mpamvu yo gufata ingamba zitagomba kuvuguruzanya n'ingendo mpuzamahanga n'ubucuruzi" kandi ko "ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) ritanga inama yo kugabanya ubucuruzi n'ingendo".
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryasabye umuryango mpuzamahanga gutanga miliyoni 675 z'amadolari mu nkunga z'ingamba ziteganyijwe mu bihugu bifite amikoro make, rigaragaza ko hakenewe cyane inkunga y'ibihugu "bitafite uburyo bwo kumenya abantu banduye virusi, kabone n'iyo yaba yaragaragaye".
Tedros kandi yatanze amagambo atangaza ko "imbaraga zacu zigereranywa n'imbaraga z'umuntu ufite intege nke muri twe" kandi asaba umuryango mpuzamahanga "kushora imari uyu munsi cyangwa kwishyura igiciro kinini nyuma". Ku ya 11 Gashyantare, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS), mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru, ryise COVID-19.
Kuri uwo munsi, Tedros yatangaje ko Umunyamabanga Mukuru wa Loni, Antonio Guterres yemeye gutanga "ubushobozi bwose bw'umuryango w'abibumbye mu gusubiza".
Ibyo byatumye hashyirwaho itsinda ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku bibazo by'iki cyorezo, ryemerera ONU guhuza ibisubizo byose, kandi rizemerera OMS "gushyira imbere ibisubizo by'ubuzima mu gihe izindi nzego zishobora kwifashishwa mu kumenya ingaruka z'iki cyorezo ku bantu, ubukungu n'iterambere".
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare, itsinda ry'ubutumwa bufatanyije buyobowe na WHO hamwe n'u Bushinwa ryashyizweho kugirango rihe impuguke mpuzamahanga n'impuguke za WHO ku butaka mu Bushinwa gufasha mu buyobozi bw'aho "uburwayi n'ubwandu" binyuze mu gukorana n'amashuri n'inama n'ibigo bikomeye by'igihugu, no gukora ingendo zo ku butaka kugira ngo barebe "ingaruka z'ibikorwa byo gusubiza ku rwego rw'intara n'umujyi, harimo uturere tw'imijyi n'imidugudu". Ku ya 25 Gashyantare, WHO yatangaje ko "isi igomba gukora byinshi kugira ngo yitegure icyorezo cya coronavirus", ivuga ko kuva mu ntangiriro y'icyorezo, ibihugu bigomba kuba "mu cyiciro cyo gukira".
Mu gusubiza icyorezo cyugarije Irani, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryoherejeyo itsinda ry'abafatanyabikorwa kugira ngo barebe uko ibintu byifashe. Ku wa 28 Gashyantare, abayobozi b'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima bavuze ko igipimo cy'ibyago bya virusi ya corona ku rwego rw'isi kizazamuka kiva kuri "cyinshi" kigera kuri "cyinshi cyane", ari na cyo kigero cyo hejuru kurusha ibindi byose cyo kuburira no gusuzuma ibyago.
Mike Ryan, umuyobozi mukuru wa gahunda y'ubutabazi bw'ubutabazi bw'ibihe bidasanzwe ya OMS, mu itangazo yatanze yatanze yatanze umuburo agira ati "iki ni ikigeragezo nyacyo kuri buri butegetsi ku isi: bityo rero tugomba kwitegura.
Iyi virusi ishobora kuba iri mu nzira kandi mugomba kwitegura", yasabye ko hakorwa ingamba zo gusubiza neza zishobora gufasha isi kwirinda "ibibi kurushaho".
Ryan yavuze kandi ko amakuru ariho ubu adashobora kwemeza ko abayobozi b'ubuzima bw'abaturage batangaza ko iki cyorezo ari icyorezo ku isi, avuga ko gutangaza ko ari icyorezo bisobanura ko "dukunda kwemera ko buri muntu wese ku isi azandura iyi virusi".
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangaje ko icyorezo cya coronavirus ari icyorezo.
Umuyobozi Mukuru yavuze ko OMS "ihangayikishijwe cyane n'ibipimo biteye ubwoba by'ikwirakwira n'uburemere, n'ibipimo by'ubudahangarwa biteye impungenge". OMS yahawe ibisobanuro bikomeye ku byo babonaga ko ari ugukemura neza iki cyorezo, harimo gutinda gutangaza ko ari ikibazo cy'ubutabazi mu buzima rusange, no gushyiraho icyorezo.
Ibisubizo by'urugomo byaranzwe n'impapuro z'umwirondoro z'umukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, zisaba kwegura, zashyizweho umukono n'abantu 733.000 kuva ku ya 6 Mata.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, impuguke mu by'uburenganzira bwa muntu muri ONU zemeza ko uburenganzira bwa buri muntu bubahirizwa mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Itsinda ry'impuguke ryavuze ko buri muntu wese afite uburenganzira bwo gukora ibikorwa byo kurokora ubuzima, kandi ko leta ifite inshingano yo kubikora.
Iryo tsinda ryashimangiye ko kubura umutungo cyangwa ubwishingizi bw'ubuzima bidakwiye kuba impamvu yo gutandukanya itsinda runaka.
Abahanga bemeje ko buri wese afite uburenganzira bwo kugira ubuzima bwiza, harimo abafite ubumuga, abantu bo mu bwoko buke, abageze mu za bukuru, abatagira aho baba, abafite ibibazo by'ubuzima, abafunzwe, impunzi n'abandi bantu badashyizweho bakenera inkunga ya leta.
Imiryango mpuzamahanga ishinzwe imiyoborere irimo gukemura ingaruka z'ubukungu n'imibereho myiza y'abaturage ziterwa n'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
OEC yatangije urubuga rwo gutanga amakuru yuzuye kandi ku gihe ku bisubizo by'amabwiriza mu bihugu byo hirya no hino ku isi, hamwe n'ibitekerezo n'inama.
Kuva ku miyoborere yo gushimangira imibereho myiza y'abaturage n'ubukungu bw'isi kugeza ku guhangana n'ingaruka zo gufunga no gukumira ingendo, icyerekezo cya digitale kirimo igikoresho cyo gukurikirana politiki ya leta, kigamije gufasha ibihugu kwigira ku bindi no koroshya igisubizo cy'isi yose cy'ubwumvikane kuri coronavirus.
Leta y'Ubushinwa yanenzwe na Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, Minisitiri w'Ibiro by'Abaminisitiri w'u Bwongereza Michael Goff, na Edward Bolsonaro umuhungu wa Perezida wa Bresil Jair Bolsonaro kubera uburyo bakemuye iki cyorezo cyatangiriye mu ntara ya Hubei yo mu Bushinwa.
Abayobozi b'amashyaka ya gikomunisiti y'Ubushinwa (CPC) birukanywe mu nzego zitandukanye kubera uburyo bakemuye ibikorwa byo gushyira abantu mu kato mu Bushinwa rwagati, mu kugaragaza umujinya w'uko inzego za politiki zitabiriye icyorezo muri utwo turere.
Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo bemeza ko icyo cyemezo cyari kigamije kurinda Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Ishyaka ry'Abakomunisiti ry'Ubushinwa Xi Jinping ku ndwara ya Coronavirus.
Bamwe mu bayobozi b'Abashinwa, urugero nka Zhao Lijian, banze kwemera ko icyorezo cya coronavirus cyatangiriye i Wuhan, bashyigikira ibitekerezo by'ubugambanyi byavuzwe na Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika cyangwa Ubutaliyani ku cyorezo cya COVID-19.
Ubuyobozi bwa Donald Trump muri Amerika bwise coronavirus "umugera w'Abashinwa" cyangwa "umugera wa Wuhan", buvuga ko Ubushinwa "bwategetse ko amakuru yafungwa bigatuma virusi ikomeza kuba icyorezo ku isi", bamwe mu banenga bavuga ko ari ivangura "kandi ko [ibyiyumvo] byirengagijwe ku kuba ubutegetsi bwe bwananiwe guhagarika iyi ndwara".
Daily Beast yabonye telegaramu ya leta ya Amerika isuzuma gahunda y'itumanaho n'ibikoresho by'ibanze byo mu kanama k'umutekano, ivuga mu buryo bw'ingamba ko "byose bifitanye isano n'Ubushinwa.
Twasabwe gushakisha no gukwirakwiza ubutumwa mu buryo bwose bushoboka, harimo amateraniro y'abanyamakuru no kugaragara kuri televiziyo. "Ibitangazamakuru nka Politico, Foreign Policy na Bloomberg byavuze ko imihati y'Ubushinwa yo kohereza imfashanyo mu bihugu byibasiwe na virusi ari kimwe mu bikorwa by'ubukangurambaga bwo kugira ingaruka ku isi.
Umuyobozi ushinzwe politiki y'amahanga w'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi, Joseph Borel, yaburiye ko hari "igice cya politiki gihanitse kirimo urugamba rwo kugira uruhare mu bikorwa byo guhungabanya no kugoreka".
Borrell kandi yavuze ko "Ubushinwa bufite ubutumwa bukomeye bw'uko, bitandukanye na Amerika, ari umufasha ufite inshingano kandi wizewe".
Ubushinwa kandi bwasabye Amerika gukuraho ibihano kuri Siriya, Venezuela na Irani, mu gihe byatangajwe ko bwohereje imfashanyo muri ibyo bihugu bibiri bya nyuma.
Ibihano bya Amerika byabujije Jack Ma gutanga udupfukamunwa 100.000 muri Cuba ku itariki ya 3 Mata.
Abategetsi ba Amerika kandi bashinjwaga ko bohereje mu gihugu cyabo imfashanyo zari zigenewe ibindi bihugu.
Hari kandi n'amakimbirane y'ibanga yavuzwe mu bindi bihugu, urugero nk'u Budage, Otirishiya, U Busuwisi, Repubulika ya Tchèque n'u Butaliyani.
Byongeye kandi, Turukiya yafashe ibikoresho bihumeka by'imashini amagana byari bigenewe muri Esipanye.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, leta y'Ubutaliyani yanenze ko EU itagaragariza ubufatanye Ubutaliyani bwazahajwe na coronavirus.
Mauritsu Massari, Ambasaderi w'Ubutaliyani muri EU, yagize ati "Ubushinwa bwitabiriye gusa ku rwego rw'ibihugu byombi.
Birumvikana ko ibyo atari ikimenyetso cyiza cy'ubwiyunge bw'u Burayi".
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, nyuma y'ijambo rya telefoni yagiranye na Minisitiri w'Intebe w'Ubutaliyani, Giuseppe Conte, Perezida w'Uburusiya Vladimir Putin yateguriye igisirikare cy'Uburusiya kohereza abaganga ba gisirikare, imodoka zihariye zo guhanagura indwara, n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Butaliyani.
Ikinyamakuru cyo mu Butaliyani cyitwa La Stampa cyasubiyemo "umuntu ukomeye mu bya politiki" utavuzwe izina, avuga ko 80 ku ijana by'imfashanyo z'u Burusiya "zitagira icyo zamarira u Butaliyani cyangwa ngo zigire icyo zimumarira".
Uwatangaga amakuru yashinje Uburusiya gutangiza igitero cya "Politiki na dipolomasi" Laft.
Perezida wa Lombardy, Atilio Fontana, na Minisitiri w'Ububanyi n'Amahanga w'Ubutaliyani Luigi Di Maio bahakanye ibivugwa n'abanyamakuru, maze bagaragaza ko bishimiye ibyo bakoze.
U Burusiya kandi bwohereje indege itwara ibicuruzwa by'ubuvuzi muri Amerika.
Umuvugizi wa Kremlin, Dmitry Peskov, yavuze ko "mu gufasha bagenzi be b'Abanyamerika, [Putin] atekereza ko igihe ibigo by'Abanyamerika bikora ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'ibikoresho bizongera gukora, na byo bizashobora gusubiza ibyiza bibaye ngombwa".
Imyitozo ya gisirikare ya NATO "Gun 2020" izakorerwa mu Budage, Polonye, n'ibihugu bya Baltique, ni yo myitozo ya gisirikare ikomeye cyane NATO izakora kuva intambara y'ubutita irangiye.
Umunyamabanga Mukuru wa Campaign for Nuclear Disarmament Kate Hudson yanenze imyitozo ya Gunners 2020 agira ati: "Mu gihe cy'ibibazo by'ubuzima rusange biriho, imyitozo ntabwo iteza akaga ubuzima bw'abasirikare ba Amerika n'ibihugu byinshi by'i Burayi biyifatanyamo gusa ahubwo kandi n'abaturage b'ibihugu bizayigwamo". Guverinoma ya Irani yahuye cyane na virusi, aho abanyamuryango bagera kuri makumyabiri b'inteko ishinga amategeko hamwe n'abandi banyapolitiki cumi na batanu bahoze cyangwa bariho ubu.
Perezida wa Irani Hassan Rouhani yandikiye abayobozi b'isi ibaruwa rusange ku ya 14 Werurwe 2020 asaba ubufasha, avuga ko igihugu cye kirimo kugorwa no kurwanya iki cyorezo kubera ko kitagera ku masoko mpuzamahanga kubera ibihano bya Amerika kuri Irani. Iki cyorezo cyateye Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gusaba ko hashyirwaho politiki z'imibereho myiza zisanzwe mu bindi bihugu bikize, harimo ubwisungane mu kwivuza, kwita ku bana bose, ikiruhuko cy'umuryango gihemba, n'amafaranga menshi y'ubuzima rusange.
Abasesenguzi mu bya politiki biteze ko bishobora kugira ingaruka mbi ku mahirwe ya Donald Trump yo kongera gutorwa mu matora ya perezida ya 2020. Imishyikirano ya dipolomasi hagati y'u Buyapani na Koreya y'Epfo yarushijeho kuzamba kubera icyorezo.
Koreya y'Epfo yanenze "imihati yo gushyira abantu mu kato idasobanutse kandi idashyize mu gaciro" y'u Buyapani nyuma y'aho u Buyapani butangaje ko umuntu wese uzava muri Koreya y'Epfo azashyirwa mu kato mu byiciro bya leta by'ibyumweru bibiri.
Mu mizo ya mbere, abaturage bo muri Koreya y'Epfo bari bafite impungenge ku byo Perezida Moon Jae-in yari yakoze muri icyo gihe cy'ihungabana.
Abanyakoreya benshi basinye impapuro zisaba ko Moon yafungwa kubera ko bavuga ko leta yataye umutwe mu guhangana n'iki cyorezo cyangwa se ko yashimye uburyo yabyitabiriye. Icyorezo cyemereye ibihugu gushyiraho amategeko ajyanye n'ibihe by'ubukungu mu gihe cy'igisubizo.
Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo bavuze ko ibyo bishobora gutuma leta zikomeza kugenzura ubutegetsi.
Muri Hongiriya, inteko ishinga amategeko yatoye ko Minisitiri w'Intebe, Viktor Orban, yemererwa gutegeka mu gihe kitarondoreka, guhagarika inteko ishinga amategeko ndetse n'amatora no guhana abamamaje amakuru y'ibinyoma kuri virusi ndetse na leta mu guhangana n'ikibazo.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus cyateje ibibazo byinshi by'ibura ry'ibikoresho kubera gukoresha ibikoresho ku isi mu kurwanya icyorezo, kugura mu buryo bwo guhungabana, no guhagarika inganda n'ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi.
Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti cyatanze imiburo ku kibazo cy'ibura ry'imiti n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi bitewe n'uko abakiriya babisaba cyane kandi ababikora bakabura ibibakemurira.
Mu turere twinshi, habaye kandi ugura mu buryo bwo guhungabana, bituma ibikoresho by'ibanze by'ibikoresho by'ibanze birimo ibiribwa, impapuro z'isuku n'amacupa y'amazi, biva ku ntebe, bituma habaho ibura ry'ibikoresho.
Uruganda rw'ikoranabuhanga rwagaragaje ko rwibeshya ku gutinda kw'ibicuruzwa bya elegitoroniki.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, ibyifuzo by'ibikoresho byo kwirinda bishobora kwiyongera inshuro 100.
Ibyo byatumye ibiciro byiyongeraho inshuro 20 ugereranyije n'ibisanzwe, kandi bituma ibyokurya bifata amezi ari hagati ya ane na atandatu.
Nanone kandi, byatumye ku isi hose habaho ikibazo cy'ibikoresho byo kwirinda, kandi Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye Ryita ku Buzima ryaburiye ko ibyo byari gushyira mu kaga abakozi bo mu rwego rw'ubuzima.
Muri Ositaraliya, icyorezo cyatumye abacuruzi ba Diego babona uburyo bushya bwo kugurisha ibicuruzwa bya Ositaraliya mu Bushinwa.
Ubu bukangurambaga bwatumye amata y'abana aba make mu masuporari amwe n'amwe, nyuma y'aho leta ya Ositaraliya irayabuza. Nubwo hari abantu benshi banduye COVID-19 mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani no mu karere ka Wuhan, ndetse n'ibyifuzo by'ibiribwa byakurikiyeho, utwo turere twombi twaracitse intege kubera ibura ry'ibiribwa.
Ingamba zashyizweho n'u Bushinwa n'u Butaliyani zo kurwanya kubika ibinyabuzima no kubikoresha mu buryo butemewe n'amategeko, zagiye zisohoza neza gahunda yo kwirinda ibura ry'ibiribwa mu Burayi no muri Amerika ya Ruguru.
Amajyaruguru y'u Butaliyani, aho ubuhinzi bukomeye, ntiyagize igisebo gikomeye, ariko ibiciro bishobora kuzamuka nk'uko abahagarariye inganda babitekereza.
Amashami y'ibiribwa yari acitse burundu, ndetse no mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu gihe abayobozi ba leta y'Ubushinwa bari barekuye inyama z'ingurube kugira ngo abaturage bahabwe ibyokurya bihagije.
Mu Butaliyani, hari amategeko nk'ayo asaba abahinzi b'ibiribwa kubika ibyokurya mu gihe habaye ibintu nk'ibyo byihutirwa.
Ubushinwa bwumvise ingaruka ku bukungu bw'isi: Nk'uko raporo y'itangazamakuru yo ku wa 16 Werurwe ibigaragaza, ubukungu bw'Ubushinwa bwangijwe cyane mu mezi abiri ya mbere ya 2020 n'ingamba zafashwe na leta zo kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi, ndetse n'ubucuruzi bw'abacuruzi b'abacuruzi bamanutseho 20.5%.
Kubera ko Ubushinwa ari ikigo cy'ubukungu n'inganda, icyorezo cya virusi cyagaragaye ko ari ingorabahizi ikomeye ku mutekano w'ubukungu bw'isi.
Agatha Demaris wo mu kigo cy'ubutasi cya EIC, yavuze ko amasoko azakomeza guhungabana kugeza igihe hazaba hagiye kugaragara neza ibisubizo by'ibiza.
Muri Mutarama 2020, bamwe mu bashakashatsi bagaragaje ko ingaruka z'icyorezo ku bukungu ku bukungu bw'isi zishobora kurenga izari zitewe n'icyorezo cya SARS cyabaye hagati ya 2002 na 2004.
Impuguke muri Kaminuza ya Washington i St. Louis yavuze ko urujya n'uruza rw'ibintu ku isi yose rwashyizwe mu kaga kangana na miriyari zisaga 300 z'amadolari, kandi ko bishobora kumara imyaka ibiri.
Raporo zivuga ko Opec yabonye "ihungabana" nyuma y'uko ibiciro bya peteroli byagabanutse cyane kubera ibyifuzo bike by'Ubushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 24 Gashyantare, amasoko y'imari n'imigabane yo ku isi yose yagabanutse bitewe n'ubwiyongere bukabije bw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 hanze y'Ubushinwa.
Ku ya 27 Gashyantare, kubera impungenge zikomeje kwiyongera ku cyorezo cya coronavirus, ibipimo byinshi by'imigabane ya Amerika, harimo na Nasdaq-100, Standard & Poor's 500, na Dow Jones Industrial Average, byanditseho ibirarane bikomeye cyane kuva mu 2008, aho Dow igwaho amanota 1,191, ari na yo ibirarane bikomeye cyane mu munsi umwe kuva mu gihe cy'ihungabana ry'imari mu 2007/08.
Ibipimo bitatu byose birangiye icyumweru biri hasi cyane ku kigero cy'icumi ku ijana.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, Scop Ratings GmbH yemeje ko Ubushinwa bufite igipimo cy'ubudehe, ariko ikomeza icyizere cy'uko buzaba butameze neza.
Imigati yongeye kugwa kubera impungenge z'icyorezo cya Coronavirus, aho yagabanutse cyane ku itariki ya 16 Werurwe.
Abantu benshi batekereza ko ubukungu buzagabanuka.
Umuhanga mu by'ubukungu, Mohamed Al-Arian yashimye ingamba z'ubutabazi zafashwe n'amabanki nkuru n'ibihugu mu gihe gikwiye.
Amabanki nkuru y'igihugu arimo agira icyo akora vuba kurusha uko byari bimeze mu gihe cy'ihungabana ry'ubukungu rya 2008.
Urugendo ni kimwe mu bice byazahajwe cyane n'amategeko yo guhagarika ingendo, gufunga ahantu hahurira abantu benshi harimo n'ahantu hakunze kwerekezwa ba mukerarugendo, ndetse no gukangurira leta kutagira ingendo hirya no hino ku isi.
Ingaruka zabaye iz'uko kompanyi nyinshi z'indege zahagaritse ingendo kubera ko abazikeneye bagabanutse, harimo British Airways, China Eastern Airlines na Cantors, mu gihe ikigo cy'indege cyo mu Bwongereza, Flybe, cyarasenyutse.
Ingaruka ku ruganda rw'ingendo zo mu mazi zari mu rugero rutari bwigere rubaho.
Ama gari ya moshi menshi n'ibibuga by'indege na byo byafunzwe.
Iki cyorezo cyahuriranye n'igihe cy'ingendo cya Chunyun, igihe cy'ingenzi cyo gutemberera Umwaka Mushya w'Abashinwa.
Guverinoma z'igihugu n'iz'uturere zahagaritse ibikorwa byinshi by'abantu benshi, harimo ibirori byo kwizihiza Umwaka Mushya, hamwe n'amasosiyete yigenga na yo afunga amaduka yayo n'ibibuga by'ubukerarugendo nka Disneyland Hong Kong na Disneyland Shanghai.
Ibikorwa byinshi by'umwaka mushya n'ahantu hakunze kuboneka ba mukerarugendo byafunzwe kugira ngo hatabaho guterana kw'abantu benshi, harimo n'umujyi wa Beijing wahagaritswe n'amasengero gakondo.
Mu ntara 24 muri 31 zigize u Bushinwa, mu mirenge no mu turere, abategetsi bongereye igihe cy'ibiruhuko by'umwaka mushya kugeza ku itariki ya 10 Gashyantare, kandi batanga amabwiriza ku bigo byinshi by'ubucuruzi ko bitagomba kongera gufungura kugeza kuri iyo tariki.
Ibyo bice bigira 80% by'umusaruro mbumbe w'igihugu na 90% by'ibyoherezwa mu mahanga.
Hong Kong yashyize ku rwego rwo hejuru ibisubizo by'indwara zandura, yatangaje ko ari mu bihe by'ubukungu, ikomeza gufunga amashuri kugeza muri Werurwe, kandi ikuraho ibirori by'umwaka mushya. Urwego rw'ubucuruzi ku isi hose rwagize ingaruka mu kugabanya amasaha y'akazi cyangwa gufunga by'agateganyo.
Abantu bageraga ku bacuruzi bo mu Burayi no muri Amerika y'Epfo bagabanutseho 40%.
Abacuruzi bacuruzi bo muri Amerika ya Ruguru no mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati, baguye hagati ya 50 na 60%.
Ibi kandi byatumye urujya n'uruza rw'abagenzi mu maduka rucika hagati ya 33 na 43% mu kwezi kwa Werurwe ugereranyije n'ukwezi kwa Gashyantare.
Abakora amaduka ku isi hose bashyizeho ingamba z'inyongera, nko kongera isuku, gushyiraho ibikoresho byo kugenzura ubushyuhe bw'abaguzi no guhagarika ibikorwa. Komisiyo y'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ishinzwe ubukungu muri Amerika y'Epfo igaragaza ko icyorezo cy'ubukene gishobora gutuma muri Amerika y'Epfo abantu bari hagati ya miriyoni 14 na 22 bakomeza kuba mu bukene bukabije kurusha uko byari bimeze iyo hataza kuba icyorezo.
Muri Mutarama na Gashyantare 2020, mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya Wuhan, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 5 mu Bushinwa batakaje akazi.
Abakozi benshi b'abimukira bo mu cyaro b'Abashinwa bagera kuri miliyoni 300 bafunze mu ngo zabo mu ntara zo hagati mu gihugu, cyangwa mu ntara ya Hubei. Muri Werurwe 2020, Abanyamerika barenga miliyoni 10 batakaje akazi maze basaba ubufasha bwa leta.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus gishobora gutwara imirimo miliyoni 47 muri Amerika, kandi ubushomeri bushobora kugera kuri 32%, nk'uko bigereranywa na Federal Reserve Bank of St. Louis. Mu Buhinde, gufunga imirimo byasize abimukira b'Abahinde babarirwa muri za miriyoni (babona umushahara w'iminsi yose) badafite akazi. Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ikigo cya Angus Reed bwabonye ko 44% by'imiryango y'Abanyakanada yahuye n'ubushomeri bw'uburyo runaka.
Mu gice cya kabiri cya Werurwe, abakozi b'Abafaransa bagera kuri miliyoni 4 basabye inguzanyo z'ubushomeri bw'agateganyo, naho abakozi b'Abongereza bagera kuri miliyoni 1 basabye inguzanyo rusange. Mu Budage, hari abacuruzi bagera hafi kuri miliyoni imwe batumye abakozi babo gukora mu gihe gito, bakoresheje gahunda ya leta yo gufasha abakozi bita Courserbit.
Ubufaransa n'u Bwongereza byashyizeho gahunda y'ubudehe bw'akazi k'igihe gito mu Budage.
Urwego rw'ubuhanzi n'umurage w'umuco rwashenguwe cyane n'icyorezo, cyibasiye ibikorwa by'imiryango ndetse n'abantu ku isi hose, baba abakora cyangwa abikorera ku giti cyabo.
Ibigo by'ubuhanzi n'umuco byashyizeho ingufu mu gushyigikira inshingano zabyo (akenshi zishyurwa na leta) zo gutanga uburyo bwo kugera ku murage w'umuco w'abaturage, kubungabunga umutekano w'abakozi babyo n'abaturage, no gushyigikira abahanzi uko bishoboka kose.
Kugeza muri Werurwe 2020, hirya no hino ku isi, mu buryo butandukanye, amazu ndangamurage, amazu y'ibitabo, amazu y'ibitaramo n'ibindi bigo by'umuco byafunzwe by'iteka, ndetse n'ibitaramo, ibikorwa n'ibyerekanwa byabyo byakuweho cyangwa byimuriwe.
Mu gusubiza, habaye imbaraga nyinshi zo gutanga serivisi z'ubundi buryo binyuze mu buryo bwa digitale. Mu bindi byateye iyi ndwara, hari ibikorwa by'idini byahagaritswe, ibikorwa bikomeye by'imikino, n'ibindi bikorwa by'imibereho myiza, nk'iminsi mikuru y'umuziki, ibitaramo, inama z'ikoranabuhanga, n'imyidagaduro.
Uruganda rwa sinema na rwo rwagize ikibazo. Vatikani yatangaje ko ibirori by'icyumweru gitagatifu i Roma, bibera mu cyumweru cya nyuma cy'igihe cy'Icyunamo cya Gikristo mu gihe cy'Ikarema, byakuweho.
Amatorero menshi ya gikristo yasabye abantu bakuze kuguma mu rugo aho kujya mu misa ku cyumweru; amatorero amwe yatumye ibikorwa by'itorero biboneka binyuze kuri radiyo, kuri interineti cyangwa kuri televiziyo mu gihe andi atamba amasengesho atavuye mu modoka.
Kubera ko Arikiyepisikopi ya Roma yafunze insengero zayo n'urusengero rwayo, kandi akarere ka St. Peter kakurwaho abagenzi b'Abakristo, izindi nzego z'idini na zo zahagaritse imirimo n'amateraniro rusange mu nsengero, mu misigiti, mu nsengero z'Abayahudi, mu nsengero no mu Gurdwara.
Minisiteri y'Ubuzima ya Irani yatangaje ko amasengesho yo ku wa Gatanu yasubitswe mu turere twatewe n'icyorezo, nyuma yaho ibigo by'Abasiramu birafungwa, mu gihe Arabiya Sawudite yabujije abagenzi b'abanyamahanga ndetse n'abaturage bayo kujya mu bibanza byera i Maka na Madina.
Iki cyorezo cyateje ihungabana rikomeye cyane mu ngengabihe y'imikino ku isi yose kuva mu Ntambara ya Kabiri y'Isi Yose.
Imikino myinshi ikomeye yahagaritswe cyangwa isubikwa, harimo 2019-20 Champions League, 2019-20 Premier League, 2020 Europa League, 2019-20 NBA n'umwaka wa 2019-20 wa National Hockey League.
Iki cyorezo cyadindije gahunda z'imikino Olempike y'impeshyi ya 2020, yagombaga gutangira mu mpera z'ukwezi kwa karindwi, kandi Komite Olempike Mpuzamahanga yatangaje kuwa 24 Werurwe ko iyi mikino "izasubirwamo nyuma ya 2020 ariko itazatangira mu mpeshyi ya 2021". Amakipe y'imikino n'ahandi hantu ho gukinira hirya no hino ku isi byafunzwe, kandi amarushanwa y'imikino yo gukina ku giti cye yasubitswe cyangwa arakurwa.
Ibi byatumye abakinnyi benshi bahita bajya gukina kuri interineti, aho imbuga nyinshi zo gukina kuri interineti zatangaje ko habonetse ukwiyongera kwinshi kw'amafaranga y'abinjijwe. Uruganda rw'imyidagaduro na rwo rwarafashwe, aho amakipe atandukanye yahagaritswe cyangwa hakurwaho ingendo z'ibitaramo.
Amasinema menshi manini nk'ayo kuri Broadway na yo yahagaritse ibitaramo byose.
Bamwe mu bahanzi bashatse uburyo bwo gukomeza gukora no gusangira ibikorwa byabo kuri interineti nk'uburyo bwo gusimbura ibitaramo bisanzwe bikorerwa mu buryo bwa Live, nko gukora ibitaramo cyangwa gukora "ibirori" kuri interineti by'abahanzi bakora, batanga no gutangaza ibikorwa byabo.
Imyinshi mu myumvire ya internet yerekeye virusi ya corona yakwirakwiriye ku mbuga nkoranyambaga, aho benshi bahindutse urwenya n'imyidagaduro mu gihe hari imimerere idashidikanywaho.
Kuva icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatangira, abantu bafite inkomoko mu Bushinwa no muri Aziya y'Iburasirazuba, ndetse n'abantu bakomoka mu bihugu by'i Burayi, Amerika n'ibindi, bakunze kwibasirwa n'urwikekwe, kwanga abanyamahanga no kubasuzugura.
Ibikorwa byo gutinya, gushidikanya no kwanga byibonekeje mu bihugu byinshi, cyane cyane mu Burayi, Aziya y'Iburasirazuba, Amerika ya Ruguru, no mu karere ka Aziya na Pasifika.
Raporo zatanzwe muri Gashyantare (igihe abenshi mu barwayi bari bakiri mu Bushinwa) zagaragarije ibyiyumvo by'ivangura byibonekeje mu matsinda atandukanye ku isi yose ku Bushinwa bavuga ko bakwiriye virusi cyangwa ko bahabwa igihano cyemewe.
