Abashinwa kimwe n'abandi bantu bo muri Aziya bo mu Bwongereza no muri Amerika, batangaje ko hari ibikorwa by'ivangura by'amoko, ndetse n'ihohoterwa, byiyongera.
Perezida wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Donald Trump, yanenzwe kubera ko yavuze ko coronavirus ari "virusi y'Abashinwa", ijambo abanyamagambo bavuga ko ari iry'ivangura kandi ryanze Abashinwa.
Abigaragambya muri Ukraine bagabye igitero kuri bisi zitwaye Abakuvereniya n'abanyamahanga bari bavuye i Wuhan bajya i Novi-Sanzari.
Abanyeshuri baturutse mu majyaruguru y'uburasirazuba bw'u Buhinde, ku mupaka w'u Bushinwa, biga mu mijyi minini yo mu Buhinde, bahanganye n'ikibazo cyo gutotezwa kubera icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Umuyobozi w'ishyaka rya Bharatiya Janata muri leta ya Bengal y'uburengerazuba, Dilip Ghosh, yavuze ko Abashinwa basenye ibidukikije kandi ko "Imana yabihoreye".
Nyuma yaho, ambasade y'Ubushinwa i Kolkata yamaganye ayo magambo, ayita "amakosa". Mu Bushinwa, iki cyorezo cyatumye abantu banga abanyamahanga kandi bakorera ibikorwa by'ivangura ku baturage batari Abashinwa, aho abanyamahanga bafatwa nk'"ibisigazwa by'abanyamahanga" kandi bagashyirwa mu "myanya y'intoki".
Ibinyamakuru byinshi byavanye ku rubuga impapuro z'ubutumire bw'amafaranga yishyurwa ku makuru ya coronavirus cyangwa byose.
