Iperereza rya laboratwari ku ndwara ya coronavirus yo mu guhumeka 2019 (COVID-19) n'indwara ya SARS-CoV-2 ifitanye isano na yo, ririmo uburyo bwo kumenya virusi aho igaragaza udukoko tw'umubiri twangiza indwara.
RT-PCR yemeza ko habonetse virusi mu bipimo, aho ADN ya RNA ya coronavirus iboneka.
Iki kizamini kirimo amakuru y'ukuri kandi kigamije gusa kureba ADN ya SARS-CoV-2.
Ikoreshwa mu kwemeza uburwayi buherutse cyangwa bukiriho.
Igisubizo cy'umubiri w'umuntu (ururwego rw'ubuvuzi bw'amaraso) gikoreshwa mu gupima no kugenzura abaturage.
Ibizamini by'umubiri wa muntu bigaragaza umubare w'abantu banduye, harimo n'abafite ibimenyetso byoroheje cyane ku buryo bitagomba gutangwa cyangwa batagaragaza ibimenyetso.
Ibipimo by'indwara n'iby'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri bishobora kumenyekana neza bitewe n'ibisubizo by'ibizamini.
Kubera ko ibizamini ari bike, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari gifite amakuru yizewe ku ikwirakwira rya virusi mu baturage bacyo muri Werurwe 2020.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyakoze ibizamini birenga 3% by'abaturage bacyo, kandi hari itandukaniro rinini mu mubare w'ibizamini byakozwe n'ibihugu bitandukanye.
Ibi kandi bishobora kugira ingaruka zikomeye ku mibare y'abapfa, ishobora kuba yaragurishijwe cyane mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe.
Gukoresha polymerases z'imikorere y'ubundi buryo (RRT-PCR) bishobora gukoreshwa mu gupima ibipimo by'ubuhumekero biboneka mu buryo butandukanye, harimo gupima mu mazuru cyangwa gupima mu mazuru.
Ibisubizo ubusanzwe biboneka mu masaha make kugeza ku minsi ibiri.
RT-PCR ikoreshwa mu gupima mu muhogo, iba igomba gukorwa mu cyumweru cya mbere cy'indwara gusa.
Virusi ishobora kuva mu muhogo nyuma yaho ikomeza kwiyongera mu bihaha.
Ku bantu banduye bagenzurwa mu cyumweru cya kabiri, icyakorwa ni ugutora urugero rw'umuyoboro wo mu nda w'ubuhumekero mu buryo bw'umwotsi cyangwa se bakoresheje umuti wo gukorora (pelletiform).
Imwe mu miti ya mbere ya PCR yatangijwe i Charité mu mujyi wa Berlin muri Mutarama 2020 ikoresheje uburyo bwo kuvura bwa polymerases (RRT-PCR), ikaba ari yo yashyizeho urufatiro rw'ibikoresho 250,000 by'igerageza byatanzwe n'ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS).
Ubwongereza nabwo bwakoze ikizamini ku ya 23 Mutarama 2020. Ikigo cyo muri Koreya y'Epfo Kogenebiotech cyakoze igikoresho cyo gupima virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 (PowerChek Coronavirus) cyakoreshejwe mu buvuzi kandi gifite umutekano, gishingiye kuri PCR ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020.
Mu Bushinwa, BGI Group ni yo yabaye iya mbere mu kubona uruhushya rw'ibanze rw'ikoreshwa ry'ibikoresho bya SARS-CoV-2 by'ikoranabuhanga bishingiye kuri PCR, mu rwego rw'ubuyobozi bw'igihugu bw'ibicuruzwa by'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa. Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya indwara (CDC) gitanga imashini yo gupima virusi ya corona 2019 (NCoV-2019) ishingiye kuri RT-PCR ihita ikoreshwa mu bigo by'ubuvuzi binyuze mu kigo mpuzamahanga gitanga ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga.
Imwe mu miti itatu ya ADN yo mu mashini za kera z'ibanze yatumye haboneka ibisubizo bidatanga icyizere kubera ko hari ibyangiritse mu bimenyetso, kandi yatumye habaho gutinda mu cyiciro kimwe cy'igerageza mu kindi muri CDC i Atlanta; byatumye hakorwa igerageza ry'ibipimo munsi ya 100 ku munsi ku munsi mu kwezi kwa Gashyantare 2020.
Ibizamini bikoresha uturemangingo by'ubuziranenge ntibyari byemewe kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020, kandi kugeza icyo gihe, ibizamini by'igihugu n'ibikorwaremezo by'ibanze ntibyari byemerewe gutangira.
Ikigo gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti cyemeje ibizamini hakurikijwe uburenganzira bwo gukoresha mu bihe by'ubukangurambaga.
Ku ya 5 Werurwe 2020, LabCorp yatangaje ko igerageza rya COVID-19 ryashyizwe ku isoko mu gihugu cyose rishingiye kuri RT-PCR.
Mu buryo nk'ubwo, Quest Diagnostics yatumye ibizamini bya COVID-19 byashoboka mu gihugu hose guhera ku itariki ya 9 Werurwe 2020.
Nta mbogamizi z'umubare zatangajwe; ingero zigomba gukusanywa no gutunganywa hakurikijwe ibisabwa na CDC.
Mu Burusiya, ikigo cya Leta gishinzwe ubushakashatsi ku mikorobe n'ikoranabuhanga mu binyabuzima cyakoze ikigeragezo cya COVID-19 cyitwa Victor.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, Urwego rw'Igihugu Rushinzwe Ubuzima rwashyize ahagaragara ibizamini. Ku ya 12 Werurwe 2020, byatangajwe ko Mayo Clinic yakoze ibizamini byo kumenya ubwandu bwa COVID-19. Ku ya 13 Werurwe 2020, ROSH Diagnostics yahawe uruhushya na FDA rw'ibizamini bishobora gukorwa mu masaha 3.5 ku mubare munini, byemerera imashini imwe gukora ibizamini bigera kuri 4128 mu masaha 24.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe 2020, FDA yahaye uruhushya rwo gukoresha mu buryo bwihutirwa (EUA) Laboratories za Abbott gukora igerageza kuri sisitemu ya Abbott m2000; FDA yahaye uruhushya nk'urwo Hologic, Lab Corp na Thermo Fisher Scientific.
Ku ya 21 Werurwe 2020, Sevid yahawe uruhushya rwo gukoresha mu buryo bwihutirwa nk'urwo na FDA mu gupima iminota 45 gusa.
Ikigo gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti cyemeje ko hakorwa igerageza rikoresha uburyo bwo kongerera DNA ubushyuhe mu mwanya wa PCR.
Kubera ko ibyo bidasaba ko habaho imibare y'ubushyuhe ikurikirana, ubwo buryo bushobora gutanga ibisubizo byiza mu gihe kitarenze iminota itanu, n'ibisubizo bibi mu gihe kitarenze iminota 13.
