Gukaraba intoki (cyangwa gukaraba intoki), nanone bizwi nka isuku y'intoki, ni igikorwa cyo gukaraba intoki mu rwego rwo gukuraho imyanda, ibinure, mikorobe cyangwa ibindi bintu bidakenewe.
Gukaraba intoki buri gihe n'isabune mu "bihe by'ingenzi" mu gihe cy'umunsi bibuza ikwirakwira ry'indwara nyinshi, urugero nk'ibicurane na kolera, zikwirakwira mu kanwa.
Abantu bashobora kandi kwandura indwara z'ubuhumekero, urugero nk'ibicurane cyangwa ibicurane, mu gihe badakarabye intoki mbere yo gukora ku maso, ku zuru cyangwa ku munwa (ni ukuvuga mu maso).
Ibihe bitanu by'ingenzi mu munsi aho gukaraba intoki n'isabune ari ngombwa: mbere na nyuma yo guteka, nyuma yo gusukura umwana cyangwa guhindura ibishishwa, mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya, mbere yo gutegura cyangwa gukorana n'inyama, amafi cyangwa inkoko zidakara, na nyuma.
Niba nta mazi n'isabune biboneka, ushobora gukaraba intoki ukoresheje ivu.
Mbere yo gutegura, mu gihe cyo gutegura, na nyuma yo gutegura.
Mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku muntu urwaye.
Nyuma yo guhindura umwana indobo cyangwa kumuhanagura nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero.
Nyuma yo gukaraba amazuru, cyangwa gukorora, cyangwa gukorora.
Nyuma yo gukora ku matungo, ku biribwa byayo cyangwa ku myanda yayo.
Isuku y'amaboko yerekeza ku bikorwa by'isuku bifitanye isano n'ubuvuzi.
Gukaraba intoki mbere yo gutanga imiti cyangwa kwitabwaho n'abaganga bishobora gukumira cyangwa kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
Intego nyamukuru yo gukaraba intoki mu buvuzi ni ukuzikuraho ibintu byandura indwara (bakteriya, virusi cyangwa ibindi binyabuzima bishobora gutera indwara) n'ibikoresho bya shimi bishobora kwangiza cyangwa gutera indwara.
Ibyo ni ingenzi cyane cyane ku bantu bakora mu by'ibiribwa cyangwa mu by'ubuvuzi, ariko ni ingenzi no ku bantu muri rusange.
Gukaraba intoki bifite akamaro kanini ku buzima, harimo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'ibicurane, virusi ya corona, n'izindi ndwara zandura, kwirinda indwara zandura ziterwa n'ibicurane, no kugabanya ubwandu bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero.
Kugabanya umubare w'abana bapfa babyariye mu ngo.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2013 bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki neza bishobora gutuma abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu barushaho gukura.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, abana bapfa bazize indwara z'ubuhumekero n'ibicurane bashobora kugabanywa binyuriye mu kugira ibintu byoroheje bahindura mu myitwarire, urugero nko gukaraba intoki bakoresheje isabune.
Icyo gikorwa cyoroshye gishobora kugabanya umubare w'abapfa bazize izo ndwara hafi 50%.
Ingamba zo gushishikariza abantu gukaraba intoki zishobora kugabanya indwara z'ibicurane hafi na kimwe cya gatatu, nk'uko amazi meza aboneka mu duce dufite abaturage bake.
Kugabanya ibice 48% by'ibicurane bishobora guterwa no gukaraba intoki n'isabune. Gukaraba intoki n'isabune ni bwo buryo bwonyine bw'ingirakamaro kandi buhendutse bwo kwirinda ibicurane n'indwara z'ubuhumekero (ARIs) iyo imyitwarire y'ubwikunde ikurikizwa mu ngo, mu mashuri no mu baturage hirya no hino ku isi.
Indwara y'ibihaha, imwe mu ndwara zikomeye z'ubuhumekero, ni yo ihitana abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu, ihitana abana bagera kuri miriyoni 1.8 buri mwaka.
Indwara y'ibicurane n'uburwayi bw'ibihaha, hamwe bihitana abana bagera kuri miriyoni 3.5 buri mwaka.
Nk'uko bivugwa na UNICEF, gukaraba intoki n'isabune mbere yo kurya no nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero bishobora gukiza abantu benshi kurusha inkingo cyangwa ubundi buryo ubwo ari bwo bwose bwo kuvura, bikanagabanya impfu ziterwa n'ubushye bw'ibihaha hafi icya kabiri, n'iziterwa n'indwara z'ubuhumekero zikomeye zikagera kuri kimwe cya kane.
Akenshi gukaraba intoki bijyanirana n'ibindi bikorwa by'isuku mu rwego rw'ibikorwa by'isuku (amazi, isuku n'isuku).
Gukaraba intoki kandi birinda indwara z'ibicurane zikwirakwira binyuze mu gushyikirana n'umubiri.
Gukaraba intoki bigira ingaruka nke cyane kuko gukaraba intoki kenshi bishobora kwangiza uruhu kubera ko rwumye.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe muri Danimarike mu 2012 bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki cyane bishobora gutuma umuntu agira ikibazo cy'uruhu cyitwa eczema y'intoki cyangwa se indwara y'uruhu rw'intoki, cyane cyane mu bakozi b'ubuzima.
Gukaraba intoki cyane na byo akenshi bifatwa nk'ikimenyetso cy'indwara yo guhangayika bikabije (OCD).
Hari ibihe bitanu by'ingenzi mu munsi aho gukaraba intoki n'isabune ari ngombwa kugira ngo umuntu atagerwaho n'indwara z'ubwonko: nyuma yo gukaraba (gusasa, guteka, gukaraba umwana, guhindurira umwana indyo, mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya, mbere/nyuma yo gutegura ibiryo cyangwa gukorana n'inyama, amafi cyangwa inkoko zikiri nzima.
Mu bindi bihe, umuntu agomba gukaraba intoki neza kugira ngo yirinde kwandura indwara, urugero mbere cyangwa nyuma yo kuvura igisebe cyangwa igikomere, nyuma yo kwitsamura, gukorora cyangwa gukaraba amazuru, nyuma yo gukora ku myanda y'amatungo cyangwa kuyitwara, no nyuma yo gukora ku myanda.
Mu bihugu byinshi, umubare w'abantu bakaraba intoki bakoresheje isabune uragenda ugabanuka.
Ubushakashatsi ku gukaraba intoki mu bihugu 54 mu 2015 bwerekanye ko ku kigereranyo, 38.7% by'ingo zikoresha isabune. Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2014 bwagaragaje ko Arabiya Sawudite ifite igipimo cyo hejuru kigera kuri 97%, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zikaba ziri hafi ya 77%, n'Ubushinwa bukaba bufite igipimo cyo hasi cya 23%. Ubu hari uburyo bwinshi bwo guhindura imyitwarire kugira ngo wongere inyungu zo gukaraba intoki n'isabune mu bihe bikenewe. Gukaraba intoki mu ruhame ku bana biga mu mashuri mu bihe by'umunsi ni imwe mu mahitamo aboneka mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere yo gushimangira imyitwarire y'abana yo gukaraba intoki.
"Gahunda y'ubwitange bw'ibanze mu by'ubuzima" yashyizweho na Minisiteri y'Uburezi muri Filipine ni urugero rw'ibikorwa by'ubufatanye bukomeye mu guteza imbere ubuzima n'uburezi by'abana.
Gucika udukoko kabiri mu mwaka, gukaraba intoki buri munsi n'isabune, no gusukura amenyo buri munsi n'ibikoresho bya fluoride, ni byo by'ingenzi muri iyi gahunda y'igihugu.
Ni na ko byagenze muri Indoneziya.
Gukoresha isabune mu mazi bituma udukoko duto duto tuva mu ruhu.
Ingaruka z'ibanze z'isabune n'ibikoresho byo gusukura ni ukugabanya inzitizi zo kubora, no kongera uburashe.
Amazi yonyine nta cyo ashobora gukora mu kuvura uruhu kubera ko ibinure na poroteyine, ari byo bigize ubutaka, bidapfa gucika mu mazi.
Ariko kandi, gutemba k'amazi ku rugero rukwiriye bifasha mu gutunganya...
Isabuni ikomeye, kubera ko ishobora kongera gukoreshwa, ishobora gutwara mikorobe yavuye mu mikoreshereze ya mbere.
Ubushakashatsi buke bwagaragaje ko za mikorobe zishobora kwandura mu isabune, bwagaragaje ko nta bushobozi zifite bwo kwandura kuko za mikorobe zishobora gukoreshwa mu gukaraba.
Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya indwara kigira kiti "gukoresha isabune mu gihe cy'ubushyuhe ni byiza kuruta gukoresha ibikoresho bitagira aho bihuriye n'ubundi buryo bwo gukoramo".
Amasabune arwanya mikorobe yashyizwe ahagaragara cyane ku bakiriya bafite ubuzima bwiza.
Kugeza ubu, nta gihamya igaragaza ko umuti cyangwa umuti wo kugabanya ubukana bw'imiti wahitamo mu kurimbura uturemwa tw'ibinyabuzima twirinda imiti.
Icyakora, isabune zirwanya mikorobe zirimo imiti isanzwe irwanya mikorobe, urugero nka triclosan, idakora ku moko menshi y'ibinyabuzima.
Bityo rero, niba isabune irwanya mikorobe idakora ku bwoko bw'imiti idashobora gukoresha mikorobe, ishobora kutagira ingaruka nk'uko igurishwa.
Uretse kugabanya umunaniro wo hejuru n'ikinyabutabire cy'uruhu, imiterere y'ibishushanyo mbonera ishobora kuba irimo aside (acetic acid, ascorbic acid, lactic acid) nk'umuyoboro wa acidification, acide benzoic ikora anti-microbial hamwe n'ibindi bimukomeza uruhu (amavuta, vitamini, menthol, ibikomoka ku bimera). Isesengura ryimbitse ryakozwe na Kaminuza ya Oregon School of Public Health ryerekanye ko isabune isanzwe ikora neza nk'isabune yabakiriya yo mu rwego rw'abaguzi irimo trichlorine ikuraho indwara kandi ikuraho za bagiteri ku ntoki.
Amazi ashyushye akwiriye gukaraba intoki ntabwo ashyushye bihagije ngo yice mikorobe.
Iyo umubiri ufite ubushyuhe bwinshi cyane, bugera kuri dogere 37.
Ariko kandi, amazi ashyushye n'isabune ni byo bikoresha neza kurusha amazi akonje n'isabune mu gukuraho amavuta kamere afata ubutaka n'udukoko.
Mu buryo bunyuranye n'uko abantu benshi babitekereza, ubushakashatsi bwa siyansi bwagaragaje ko gukoresha amazi ashyushye nta ngaruka bigira ku kugabanya ubukana bw'udukoko turi ku biganza.
Umushongi w'intoki cyangwa umuti wo kugabanya ubukana bw'intoki ni ikintu kitagira amazi cyo gukaraba intoki.
Mu mpera z'imyaka ya za 90 no mu ntangiriro z'ikinyejana cya 21, ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki bitagira amazi kandi byanduza intoki (byitwa kandi ko ari ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki bitera inzoga, ibihanagura intoki cyangwa ibicanisha intoki) byatangiye gukundwa.
Byinshi bishingiye kuri isopropyl cyangwa ethanol ihuriweho n'ikinyabutabire nka carbomer (polymers acrylic acid) muri gel, cyangwa humidifier nka glycerin mu mazi, cyangwa se imbeho kugirango byorohere gukoresha no kugabanya ingaruka zo gukama biturutse kuri alcohol.
Kongeramo poroteyine ya idorojeni yagabanyijwe bituma habaho ibikorwa byo kurwanya mikorobe. Inzoga z'amaboko ziri mu kigero cy'inzoga kiri hagati ya 60 na 95% ni zo zica mikorobe mu buryo bw'ingirakamaro.
Inzoga z'uburozi zirimbura za bagiteri, za mikorobe z'ubwoko bwinshi zidashobora gukoreshwa n'imiti (gold cluster, methiseline, na gut gut gut, vancomycin), igituntu, za virusi zimwe na zimwe (harimo virusi itera SIDA, herpes, virusi ifata imyakura, virusi z'amaso, impyiko, ibicurane, indwara y'umwijima), n'imibembe.
Inzoga z'inzoga zirimo 70% by'inzoga zirimbura 99.97% (kugabanuka kwa logaritmu ya 3.5, kimwe no kugabanuka kwa decibel ya 35) za bagiteri ku biganza nyuma y'amasegonda 30 zishyiriweho na 99.99% kugeza kuri 99.999% (kugabanuka kwa logaritmu hagati ya 4 na 5) za bagiteri ku biganza nyuma y'umunota 1 zishyiriweho. Inzoga z'amaboko zirwanya cyane bagiteri ariko ntizibashe kurwanya virusi zimwe na zimwe.
Inzoga z'intoki ntizikora neza ku ndwara ya Norovirus (cyangwa Norwalk), ikaba ari yo mpamvu ikunze gutera indwara y'igifu n'amaraso.
Ujye ukaraba imbere n'inyuma y'amaboko, hagati y'intoki zose n'impande zayo, mu gihe cy'amasegonda agera kuri 30 kugeza amazi, ibishashi cyangwa umutobe bikamye.
Inshinge z'intoki zigomba kandi gukaraba neza, kandi zikayungururwa mu byuma byombi. Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya indwara n'irinda indwara (CDC) gitanga inama yo gukaraba intoki ukoresheje umuti uhumanya imyakura, cyane cyane iyo intoki zanduye cyane.
Gukoresha cyane ibi bikoresho by'isuku biterwa n'uko byoroshye kubikoresha kandi ko byihutira kurandura udukoko duto; ariko, ntibigomba gusimbura gukaraba intoki neza keretse gusa amazi n'isabune bibaye bidahari.
Gukoresha kenshi imiti yo kugabanya ubukana bw'intoki ikoreshwa n'inzoga bishobora gutuma uruhu ruguma rugaye, keretse iyo hari imyambaro yo kumena cyangwa imyambaro yo kumena imyanda cyangwa byombi byongerewe mu buryo bw'ibikoresho.
Ingaruka z'inzoga ku ruhu rwumye zishobora kugabanywa cyangwa gukurwaho binyuriye mu kongeramo glycerin cyangwa ibindi bintu by'imvura cyangwa byombi.
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko imiti yo gukaraba intoki irimo inzoga ituma uruhu rutera uburibwe kandi rugakomoka cyane kurusha isabune cyangwa imiti yo gukaraba.
Biragoye cyane ko umuntu agira indwara y'uruhu, indwara yo mu nda cyangwa se indwara yo kumva inzoga cyangwa ibintu byongera ku mazi yo mu bikoresho byo gukaraba intoki.
Kuba abantu barwara indwara z'uruhu ziterwa n'ubushye cyangwa se iziterwa n'ubushye, byagiye bituma abantu barushaho kugira ibyishimo, ugereranyije no gukaraba intoki n'isabune.
Nubwo ibikoresho by'isuku bitagira amazi ari ingirakamaro, ntibikuraho imyanda mu biganza, ahubwo byibasira gusa.
Kubera iyo mpamvu, imiti yo kugabanya ubukana bw'intoki ntiyafasha cyane mu gukumira ikwirakwira ry'indwara nyinshi nk'uko isabune n'amazi bifasha, kuko izo ndwara ziguma ku ntoki.
Uburyo umuti uhanagura intoki udafite inzoga ukora ahanini bishingiye ku bikoresho n'imiterere, kandi mu mateka, nta ngaruka nyinshi ugira ugereranyije n'uw'inzoga.
Vuba aha, ibishushanyo bikoresha benzalkonium chloride byagaragaye ko bifite ingaruka zikomeza kwiyongera nk'indwara zandura nyuma yo gukoreshwa, bitandukanye n'inzoga yagaragaye ko igira ingaruka nke nyuma yo gukoreshwa kenshi, wenda bitewe n'ingaruka z'imikorere mibi y'uruhu.
Abantu benshi bo mu baturage bafite amikoro make ntibashobora kugura isabune, ahubwo bakoresha ivu cyangwa ivumbi.
Umukungugu cyangwa ivu bishobora kugira ingaruka nziza kurusha amazi yonyine, ariko bishobora kuba nta ngaruka bigira ku isabune.
Hari impungenge ko iyo ubutaka cyangwa ivu byanduye mikorobe bishobora gutuma indwara zikwirakwira aho kugabanya.
Nanone kandi, nk'uko bimeze ku isabune, ivu ni umuti uhumanya umubiri kuko iyo rihuye n'amazi riba rifite umuti ufite ubushobozi bwo guhumanya.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatanze inama yo gukoresha ivu cyangwa umusenyi aho gukoresha isabune mu gihe nta yo wabona.
Uburyo bwiza bwo gukaraba intoki, buvugwa n'Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika Gishinzwe Kurwanya Indwara, bugamije gukumira ikwirakwira ry'indwara, burimo ibi bikurikira:
Jya wima intoki mu mazi ashyushye cyangwa akonje.
Gukoresha amazi atemba ni byiza kuko imisarani ishobora kuba ihumanyijwe, kandi ubushyuhe bw'amazi ntibugaragarira ko hari icyo buhindura.
Kora umutobe ku biganza byawe ubimese n'isabune nyinshi, ushyireho n'ibiganza byawe, hagati y'intoki n'amaboko yawe.
Isabuni ikuraho udukoko twanduye ku ruhu, kandi ubushakashatsi bugaragaza ko abantu bakunda gukaraba intoki neza iyo bakoresha isabune aho gukoresha amazi gusa.
Fata nibura amasegonda 20.
Iyo ukomeje gukaraba, bituma habaho guhanagura, bigatuma udukoko duto duto dukurwa mu ruhu, kandi iyo ukomeje gukaraba, urushaho gukuraho utundi dukoko.
Jya ukaraba neza munsi y'amazi arimo gutemba.
Gukaraba intoki mu kibindi bishobora kongera kwanduza.
Jya ukaraba neza cyangwa se ureke bikomere mu kirere.
Ibice bikunze kwirengagizwa ni ikiganza, intoki, hagati y'intoki n'amaboko, n'amaboko ari munsi y'amano.
Inzara z'ibumba n'amabara y'ibumba bishobora kuba birimo udukoko duto cyane.
Akenshi, ni byiza gukoresha umuti w'amavuta yo gukaraba kugira ngo udakomanga intoki, kuko iyo intoki zikometse bishobora kwangiza uruhu, bigatuma habaho ibyago byo kwandura.
Amahitamo atandukanye y'igiciro gito ashobora gutangwa mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, aho amazi ya tap, isabune cyangwa byombi bitagera, nko kuvoma amazi mu nkono ifunze cyangwa ifite imyobo ikwiriye, cyangwa gukoresha ivu iyo bibaye ngombwa. Mu bice bifite amazi make (nk'amashuri cyangwa uturere tw'icyaro mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere), hari ibisubizo byo guhuza amazi, nk'amazi ya tappi n'andi mahitamo y'igiciro gito.
