Kumesa neza intoki ni kimwe mu bintu by'ingenzi mu isuku y'intoki, ariko hari impaka ku buryo bwo kumesa neza mu byumba bya rusange.
Ubushakashatsi bwinshi bugaragaza ko amasahani y'impapuro ari meza kurusha imashini z'amashanyarazi zo kumesa intoki ziri mu byumba byinshi by'amazi.
Mu mwaka wa 2008, Kaminuza ya Westminster mu mujyi wa Londres yakoze ubushakashatsi, buyobowe n'ikigo cy'ubushakashatsi ku byerekeye imyenda y'ibishushanyo mbonera by'ibishushanyo mbonera by'ibishushanyo mbonera by'ibishushanyo mbonera by'ibishushanyo mbonera by'ibishushanyo mbonera by'ibishushanyo mbonera, kugira ngo bagereranye ibipimo by'isuku bitangwa n'ibishushanyo mbonera by'ibishushanyo mbonera by'ibishushanyo mbonera, n'ibishushanyo mbonera by'ibishushanyo mbonera by'ibishushanyo mbonera by'ibishushanyo mbonera by'ibishushanyo mbonera by'ibishushanyo mbonera.
Nyuma yo gukaraba intoki no kuzisukura mu cyuma gikonjesha umwuka, basanze umubare w'ibinyabutabire byose ku ntoki wiyongereyeho 194% ku kigero cy'ubwoko, naho ku kiganza wiyongereyeho 254%.
Gukata ukoresheje umwotsi wo kumesa byongereye umubare w'ibinyabutabire ku munwa ku kigero cya 42% no ku kiganza ku kigero cya 15%.
Nyuma yo gukaraba intoki no kuzisukura hakoreshejwe umwenda w'impapuro, umubare w'ibinyabutabire ku ntoki wagabanutseho 76%, naho ku ntoki wagabanutseho 77%. Abahanga bakoze n'ibizamini kugira ngo bamenye niba hari ibyago byo kwanduza abandi bakoresha ubwiherero n'aho babukoresha bitewe n'uburyo bw'umwimerere bwo kumesa.
Umutaka utuma umwuka usohoka mu cyumba ku muvuduko wa metero 180 ku isaha (650 km/h; 400 mph), ushobora guhumeka udukoko duto mu ntoki no mu gikoresho, kandi ushobora kwanduza abandi bakoresha ubwiherero n'aho babwugiramo mu metero ebyiri.
Gukoresha igikoma cy'umwuka ushyushye byatuma udukoko duto duto tuva muri icyo gikoma ku metero 0.25 uvuye aho kiri.
Amasahani y'impapuro ntiyagaragaje ikwirakwira ry'ibinyabuzima. Mu mwaka wa 2005, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na TÜV Produkt und Umwelt bwashyize mu gaciro uburyo butandukanye bwo kumesa intoki.
