Hari abahanga benshi bakora imashini zo kumesa intoki, kandi ubu bakoresha imashini zo kumesa intoki zikoreshwa mu kumesa impapuro.
Gukaraba intoki ukoresheje umufuka wo gukaraba intoki ni ubundi buryo bwo gukora urugendo kubera ko nta sabuni n'amazi biboneka.
Umushongi w'amaboko urimo inzoga ugomba kuba ufite nibura inzoga zingana na 60%.
Gukaraba intoki mu gihe cy'ubuvuzi byabaye itegeko igihe kirekire nyuma y'aho umuganga w'Umuhungari Agnates Simmelweis avumbuye ko ari ingirakamaro (mu 1846) mu kwirinda indwara mu bitaro.
Hariho ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki bitanga ibisobanuro byo kwibutsa abakozi b'ibitaro gukaraba intoki mu gihe bibaye ngombwa ko bibagirwa.
Ubushakashatsi bumwe bwagaragaje ko gukoresha imiti yo mu rwego rwo hejuru byagabanyije ubwandu.
Gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'ubuvuzi bigomba kumara nibura amasegonda 15, ukoresheje isabune nyinshi n'amazi cyangwa gel yo gukora uduhu, hanyuma ukamesa buri gice cy'intoki.
Ibiganza bigomba gukorakora hamwe, intoki zikagendana.
Niba hari ibisigazwa munsi y'amano, ushobora gukoresha umufuka w'ubwoya kugira ngo ubikureho.
Kubera ko mikorobe zishobora kuguma mu mazi y'amaboko, ni ngombwa ko uyashyiramo amazi meza kandi ukayomesha akayabo gasukuye.
Nyuma yo gukama, ugomba gukoresha umufuka w'impapuro mu gufunga amazi (kandi ufungure urugi rw'irembo niba ari ngombwa).
Ibyo bituma udasubira kwanduzwa n'ibyo bisenge.
Intego yo gukaraba intoki mu kigo nderabuzima ni ukuvanaho udukoko dutera indwara ("mikorobe") no kwirinda ko twanduza abandi.
Ikinyamakuru cy'ubuvuzi cyo mu Bwongereza cyatangaje ko gukaraba intoki bikiri ku kigero kitemewe mu bigo byinshi by'ubuvuzi, aho abaganga benshi bibagirwa gukaraba intoki buri gihe mbere yo gukora ku barwayi, bigatuma habaho ubwandu bw'udukoko duto.
Ubushakashatsi bumwe bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki neza n'ibindi bikorwa byoroheje bishobora kugabanya indwara z'amaraso zifitanye isano n'inkondo ya catheter ku kigero cya 66 ku ijana, kandi Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryasohoye inyandiko igaragaza uko bakaraba intoki n'uko bazikaraba mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi.
Inyandiko y'ibanze y'ubuyobozi bw'isuku y'amaboko yatanzwe na OMS, na yo iboneka ku rubuga rwayo, ku buryo abantu bashobora kuyireba.
Whitby n'abandi bakoze ubushakashatsi bw'ingirakamaro.
Ibikoresho by'ubucuruzi bishobora gupima no kugenzura isuku y'amaboko, niba ari ngombwa kugaragaza ko byubahiriza amategeko agenga imikoreshereze y'amaboko.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima rifite "Ibihe bitanu" byo gukaraba intoki:
Nyuma yo kwanduzwa amaraso/iminyunyu yo mu mubiri
Mbere yo gukora igikorwa cyo kuboneza urubyaro,
Nyuma yo kwita ku barwayi, kongera imyanda isukura mu isabune ("imiti" cyangwa "imibu") byongera ikintu cyicisha ku bikoresho byo gukaraba intoki.
Iyi nkingo ishobora gukenerwa mbere yo kubagwa cyangwa ahantu higanje udukoko twangiza ubuzima. Iyo umuntu "atetse" intoki ze kugira ngo abazwe, bisaba ko ahabwa akuma gashobora guhagarara cyangwa gukoreshwa ntawe ukimukoramo, agakoresho gashya k'ibinyabutabire cyangwa iodine, impapuro z'ibumba zo gukaraba intoki nyuma yo gukaraba, agashyimbo k'ibumba k'uburozi, n'ikindi gikoresho cy'ubutoza intoki.
Tugomba kuvanaho ibintu byose by'umurimbo.
Iyo myitozo isaba ko umuntu akaraba intoki n'amaboko kugeza ku nkokora, ubusanzwe mu minota 2 kugeza kuri 6.
Igihe kirekire cyo gusukura (iminota 10) si ngombwa.
Mu gihe cyo gukaraba, amazi agomba kurindwa kuva ku maboko agana ku ntoki.
Nyuma yo gukaraba intoki, zikomorwa n'igitambaro cy'ubumara kandi zikambikwa umwambaro wo kubaga.
Kugira ngo udakwirakwiza mikorobe, ni byiza gukaraba intoki cyangwa gukoresha umuti wo kugabanya ubukana bw'intoki mbere yo kwita ku muntu urwaye na nyuma yo kumwitaho.
Mu rwego rwo kugenzura indwara z'ibicurane mu bitaro, byaje kugaragara ko inyungu nini yo gukaraba intoki yavuye kuri 20% ya mbere yo gukaraba intoki, kandi ko hari inyungu nto cyane y'inyongera igihe bakomezaga gukaraba intoki ku kigero kirenga 35%.
Gukaraba n'isabune isanzwe bituma indwara zandura za bagiteri zikwirakwira mu biribwa inshuro zirenga eshatu ugereranyije no gukaraba n'isabune ya antibacterial. Kugenzura gukaraba intoki n'umuti urimo inzoga n'ukunywa isabune ya antibacterial mu gihe cy'amasegonda 30 ku kigereranyo, byabonye ko gukaraba inzoga byagabanyije ubwandu bwa bagiteri ku kigero cya 26% kurusha isabune ya antibacterial.
Ariko amazi n'isabune ni byo bikora neza kurusha gukaraba intoki hakoreshejwe inzoga mu kugabanya virusi ya H1N1 n'ibibyimba by'intoki. Ingamba zo kongera isuku y'intoki mu bigo nderabuzima zishobora kuba zirimo kwigisha abakozi gukaraba intoki, kongera ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki hakoreshejwe inzoga, no kubwira abakozi ubutumwa bwanditse n'ibyibutsa.
Hakenewe ubushakashatsi bwimbitse kugira ngo hamenyekane ingamba z'ingirakamaro mu bigo bitandukanye byita ku buzima.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, abantu benshi bemera ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune ari uburyo bw'ibanze kandi buhendutse bwo kugira ubuzima bwiza, kimwe n'imirire myiza.
Nyamara, kubura amazi yizewe, isabune cyangwa ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki mu ngo, mu mashuri no mu mirimo, bituma bigoye kugera ku ngeso rusange zo gukaraba intoki.
Urugero, mu bice byinshi by'icyaro muri Afurika, usanga udashobora kubona imashini zo gukaraba intoki hafi y'ubwiherero bwa bwite cyangwa bwa leta, n'ubwo hari uburyo bworoheje bwo kubaka aho bakaraza intoki.
Icyakora, kudahanagura intoki bishobora guterwa n'imyitwarire y'abantu, aho guterwa no kubura isabune cyangwa amazi.
Guteza imbere gukaraba intoki n'isabune bishobora kugira ingaruka ku myanzuro ya politiki, bikongera ubumenyi ku nyungu zo gukaraba intoki, kandi bigatuma abantu bahindura imyitwarire yabo mu gihe kirekire.
Kugira ngo ibyo bikore neza, ni ngombwa kugenzura no kugenzura.
Isuzuma ry'ubushakashatsi 70 ryabonye ko uburyo bwo mu muryango bukora mu kongera gukaraba intoki mu bihugu bifite amafaranga make cyangwa mu rwego rwo hasi, mu gihe gahunda zo kwamamaza mu rwego rw'imibereho ari nke. Urugero rumwe rwo guteza imbere gukaraba intoki mu mashuri ni "uburyo bw'inyenyeri eshatu" bwakozwe na UNICEF bwo gushishikariza amashuri gufata ingamba zoroshye kandi zitazimye zo kwemeza ko abanyeshuri bakaraba intoki bakoresheje isabune, mu bindi bisabwa n'ubuzima.
Iyo ibipimo by'ibanze byubahirijwe, amashuri ashobora kuva ku nyenyeri imwe agera ku nyenyeri eshatu amaherezo.
Kubaka ahantu ho gukaraba intoki bishobora kuba kimwe mu bikorwa byo gukangurira abantu gukaraba intoki bigamije kugabanya indwara n'urupfu rw'abana.
Umunsi Mpuzamahanga wo Gukaraba intoki ni urundi rugero rw'ubukangurambaga bwo gukangurira abantu kugira ngo bahindure imyitwarire. Kubera icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019-20, UNICEF yashishikarije abantu gukoresha ikimenyetso cyo gukaraba intoki.
Ubushakashatsi buke bwarebye ingaruka z'igiciro rusange cyo gukaraba intoki mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere n'isano bifite n'imyaka y'ubuzima igenda ihinduka bitewe n'ubumuga.
Nyamara, hari isuzuma ryagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki hakoreshejwe isabune ari byo bihenze cyane kurusha ubundi buryo bwo gukaraba amazi n'isuku.
Akamaro ko gukaraba intoki ku buzima bw'umuntu, cyane cyane ku bantu bari mu mimerere igoranye, urugero nk'ababyeyi bavuka cyangwa abasirikare bakomeretse mu bitaro, katangajwe bwa mbere mu kinyejana cya 19 n'abahanga babiri mu by'isuku y'intoki: umuganga w'Umuhungari witwaga Agnath Simmelweis wakoraga i Vienne muri Otirishiya, n'Umwongereza witwaga Florence Nightingale "washinze ubuforomo bugezweho".
Icyo gihe abantu benshi bari bagikomeza gutekereza ko indwara zaturukaga ku kirungo kibi cyitwa miasma.
Mu myaka ya za 80, indwara zandura zaturukaga ku biribwa n'indwara ziterwa n'ubuzima zatumye ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya indwara no kwirinda indwara, gitera inkunga isuku y'amaboko mu buryo bw'ingirakamaro cyane nk'uburyo bw'ingenzi bwo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
Icyorezo cy'ibicurane by'ingurube cyabaye mu mwaka wa 2009 na COVID-19 mu mwaka wa 2020 byatumye mu bihugu byinshi abantu barushaho kumenya akamaro ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune mu kwirinda izi ndwara zandura.
Urugero, mu Budage, inyandiko zifite amagambo avuga ngo "uburyo bwiza bwo gukaraba intoki" zashyizwe hafi y'ubwiherero bw'abaturage n'ubw'amazu y'ibiro n'ahantu ho gukaraba ku bibuga by'indege.
Imvugo ngo "gukaraba intoki ku kintu" isobanura ko umuntu adashaka kubazwa icyo kintu cyangwa ngo agire uruhare mu kugikora.
Iryo jambo rikomoka ku murongo wo muri Bibiliya wa Matayo aho Pilato w'Umupentekote yakarabye ibiganza bye igihe Yesu Kristo yamanikwaga ku musaraba, ariko ryamaze gukoreshwa cyane mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe by'Abongereza.
Mu mukino wa Shakespeare witwa Macbeth, Madamu Macbeth atangira gukaraba intoki cyane mu rwego rwo kugerageza gukubura ikibindi cyo mu bitekerezo cye kigaragaza ko afite icyaha cy'ibyaha yakoze n'ibyaha byashishikarije umugabo we kubikora.
Nanone kandi, byagaragaye ko iyo abantu bavuze cyangwa batekereje ku bikorwa by'ubwiyandarike, bakunda gukaraba intoki kurusha abandi, kandi bakishimira cyane ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki.
Byongeye kandi, abantu bemerewe gukaraba intoki nyuma y'iki cyigisho, ntibashobora kugira uruhare mu bindi bikorwa byo "kwisukura" by'indishyi, nk'ubwitange.
Amadini asobanura gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'isuku no mu buryo bw'ikigereranyo. Gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'ikigereranyo, hakoreshejwe amazi nta sabuni yo gukaraba intoki, ni kimwe mu birori byo gukaraba intoki byagaragariye mu madini menshi, harimo idini rya Bahá'í, idini ry'Abahindu, idini rya Tiwila, gukaraba intoki mu kiyahudi, gukaraba intoki mu Bukristo no kugenzura mu idini rya Isilamu.
