Amabwiriza yo kugenzura ibyago bya COVID-19 mu kazi
Amabwiriza yo kugenzura ibyago bya COVID-19 ku kazi ni ugushyira mu bikorwa amabwiriza yo kwirinda ibyago byo kwandura icyorezo cya Koronavirusi ya 2019 (COVID-19).
Gucunga neza ibyago mu kazi bishingiye ku kazi n'inshingano, bishingiye ku gupima ibyago bituruka ku isoko z'ubwandu, ubukana bw'indwara mu baturage, n'ibintu byugarije abakozi bashobora kwandura COVID-19.
Nk'uko byemezwa n'ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe umutekano n'ubuzima (OHSHA), akazi gafite ibyago bike byo kwandura gasaba ko abantu batagira aho bahurira n'abandi bakorana, aho usanga abantu bagirwa inama yo kwirinda kwandura, harimo gukaraba intoki, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, gukurikiza amabwiriza yo gukorora no kwitsamura, no gukomeza isuku isanzwe.
Ibikorwa bifite ibyago byo kwandura birimo ibyo bisaba ko abantu batamenyekanye cyangwa bakekwaho kwandura COVID-19 bahura kenshi cyangwa mu buryo bwa bugufi, ariko bashobora kwandura bitewe no gukwirakwiza ubwandu mu baturage cyangwa ingendo mpuzamahanga.
Ibyo bikubiyemo abakozi bagiranye imishyikirano n'abantu benshi, urugero nko mu mashuri, ahantu hakorerwa imirimo myinshi, n'ahandi hantu hacuruzwa ibintu byinshi.
Mu by'ukuri, mu gihe umuntu arwaye COVID-19, nta muntu n'umwe ushobora kurwara indwara ya COVID-19.
Urwego rw'Ubuzima n'Umutekano mu Mwuga rwemeza ko abakozi bo mu rwego rw'ubuzima n'abakora mu nzu y'ibanze bakorana n'umuntu uzwi cyangwa ukekwaho kuba afite COVID-19 bafite ibyago byo kwandura, ibyo bikaba byongera ibyago byo kwandura cyane iyo abakozi bakora ibikorwa byo guhumeka umwuka, cyangwa bagakora ibipimo by'umuntu uzwi cyangwa ukekwaho kuba afite COVID-19.
Amategeko akwiriye yo kugenzura ibyago by'abo bakozi arimo amabwiriza yo kugenzura ubwubatsi, urugero nk'ibyumba by'ubushyuhe budafite ingufu, n'ibikoresho byo kwirinda umuntu ku giti cye bikenewe mu kazi.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishobora kugira ingaruka nyinshi ku kazi.
Abakozi bashobora kuba badahari kubera uburwayi, cyangwa se kubera ko bakeneye kwitabwaho n'abandi, cyangwa se kubera ko batinya ko bashobora kuzagirirwa nabi.
Uburyo bwo gucuruza bushobora guhinduka, haba mu buryo bw'ibicuruzwa bikenewe, no mu buryo bwo kubikura (urugero, guhaha mu gihe cy'amasaha y'ikiruhuko, cyangwa binyuze mu gutanga ibicuruzwa cyangwa guhaha utashye mu modoka).
Amaherezo, ibicuruzwa bishobora guhagarara mu turere tw'isi twugarijwe cyane na COVID-19.
Iyo gahunda igaragaza ibyago biba biri mu kazi no mu kazi, hakubiyemo n'ibikomoka ku ndwara, ibyago bituruka mu rugo n'ahandi hantu, n'ibyago biba ku bakozi ku giti cyabo, urugero nk'imyaka y'iza bukuru cyangwa indwara zidakira.
Nanone kandi, bagaragaza uburyo bwo guhangana n'ibyo byago, kandi bagateganya uko bazahangana n'ibiza bishobora kuvuka.
Gutegura no gusubiza indwara zandura bishobora gukurikizwa n'inama z'igihugu cyangwa iz'amahanga.
Intego zo guhangana n'icyorezo harimo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'ubwandu mu bakozi, kurinda abantu bafite ibyago byinshi byo guhura n'ibibazo by'ubuzima, kubungabunga ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi no kugabanya ingaruka mbi ku bindi byiciro mu miyoboro yabo y'itangwa ry'ibikoresho.
