Kubera ko nta buryo bwo guca akaga ka COVID-19, uburyo bwo kugenzura neza cyane ni ubuhanga, hakurikiraho ubuyobozi, hanyuma hakurikiraho ibikoresho byo kwirinda.
Igenzura ry'ubwubatsi ririmo gukumira abakozi akaga gakomoka ku kazi, nta gushidikanya ko ari ryo ryakemura ikibazo cy'ingengo y'imari.
Amabwiriza y'ubuyobozi ni ihinduka mu mategeko y'akazi cyangwa mu bikorwa bisaba ko umukozi cyangwa umukoresha agira icyo akora.
Ibikoresho byo kurinda ubuzima (PBE) ntibikora neza nk'uko bigenzurwa n'abashinzwe kubirinda, ariko bishobora gufasha mu kwirinda ibibazo bimwe na bimwe.
Ubwoko bwose bw'ibikoresho byo kwirinda umuntu ku giti cye bigomba gutoranywa hashingiwe ku kaga umukozi ashobora guhura na ko, ku buryo bukwiriye (urugero nk'ibikoresho byo guhumeka) aho bikenewe, ku kwambara mu buryo bukwiye kandi buhoraho, ku kugenzura, kubungabunga no gusimbuza buri gihe, aho bikenewe, no kubijugunya, kubisukura no kubishyira mu bubiko, cyangwa kubitwika neza kugira ngo wirinde kwanduzwa.
Dukurikije ibivugwa n'ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe umutekano n'ubuzima (OHSHA), akazi gafite ibyago bike, kaba gasaba ko umuntu agira imishyikirano mike n'abandi bakorana.
Ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda kwandura zisabwa ku kazi kose harimo gukaraba intoki kenshi kandi mu buryo bwuzuye, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, kubahiriza amabwiriza yo gukorora no kwitsamura, harimo no gupfuka umunwa n'amazuru mu gihe bakorora no kwitsamura, gutanga udupfukamunwa n'ibikoresho by'imyanda, kwitegura gukora kure cyangwa gutegura imirimo mu gihe bibaye ngombwa, kwirinda gukoresha ibikoresho n'ibikoresho by'abandi, no gukomeza isuku no gusukura ahantu bakorera.
Gushakisha abantu bashobora kwandura vuba no kubashyira mu kato ni intambwe ikomeye mu kurinda abakozi, abakiriya, abasura n'abandi mu kazi.
Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) gitanga inama y'uko abakozi bafite ibimenyetso by'indwara ikomeye yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero baguma mu rugo kugeza umuriro, ibimenyetso by'umuriro n'ibindi bimenyetso byose birangiye nibura amasaha 24 nta miti igabanya umuriro cyangwa indi miti igabanya ibimenyetso, ko politiki z'ikiruhuko cyo kurwara zihinduka, ko abakozi bemererwa kuguma mu rugo kwita ku muntu wo mu muryango urwaye, kandi ko abakozi bamenya neza iyo politiki.
Dukurikije Itegeko rigenga umutekano n'ubuzima mu kazi, imirimo ifite ibyago byo kwandura birimo iyo isaba ko abantu batamenyekanye ko bafite cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19 bakorana imibonano mpuzabitsina kenshi cyangwa hafi cyane, mu ntera ya metero esheshatu (1.8), ariko bashobora kwandura SARS-CoV-2 bitewe n'uko ikwirakwira ry'ubwandu rikomeje mu baturage bari aho bakorera cyangwa bitewe n'uko umuntu aherutse gukora urugendo mpuzamahanga mu gace ka COVID-19.
Muri ibyo harimo abakozi basanga abantu benshi nk'uko bisanzwe mu mashuri, ahantu hakorerwa imirimo myinshi, n'ahandi hantu hacuruzwa ibintu byinshi. Mu mabwiriza yo kubishyira mu bikorwa n'amatsinda y'abakozi bafite ibyago byinshi harimo kwinjiza ibyuya by'umwuka bikora neza, kongera ibipimo by'umuyaga, gushyiraho inzitizi z'umubiri nk'ibikoresho bya plastiki by'ubushyuhe, no gushyiraho ibicuruzwa byo gufasha abakiriya bagura batagenda.
Abakozi bo muri iri tsinda ry'abafite ibyago ntibakunze gukoresha ibikoresho byo guhumeka.
Iyo umuntu arwaye ari mu ndege, ingamba zo kwirinda zikwiye zo kurinda abakozi n'abandi bantu bari mu ndege zirimo gushyira umuntu urwaye ku ntera ya metero 6, guha umwe mu bagize itsinda ry'indege kwita kuri uwo muntu urwaye, guha uwo muntu urwaye agapfukamunwa cyangwa gusaba uwo muntu urwaye ko apfuka umunwa n'amazuru ye n'utuwondo tw'impapuro mu gihe yakorora cyangwa asusumira.
Abakozi b'indege bagomba kwambara intoki z'ubuvuzi zishobora gukoreshwa igihe bahuye n'umunyeshuri urwaye cyangwa bakagira icyo bakora ku bikoresho byanduye cyangwa ku bice byanduye, kandi bashobora gukoresha ibindi bikoresho by'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri mu gihe umunyeshuri urwaye afite umuriro cyangwa se akomeza gukorora cyangwa guhumeka nabi.
Inkweto n'ibindi bintu bishobora kujugunywa bigomba kujugunywa mu mufuka w'ubwirinzi bw'ibinyabuzima, hanyuma ubutaka bwanduye bugakorwa isuku no kubohesha. Ku by'ubucuruzi, harimo ubwato bw'ingendo n'ubundi bwato bw'abagenzi, amabwiriza yo kugenzura ibyago arimo gusubika ingendo mu gihe umuntu arwaye, kwicungira ukwa wenyine no guhita abimenyesha ikigo nderabuzima cyo mu ndege mu gihe umuntu yaba afite umuriro cyangwa indi ndwara mu gihe ari mu ndege.
Mu buryo bwiza, umuntu wagombaga gukurikiranwa mu cyumba cy'umuntu wabaga ari wenyine. Ku mashuri n'ibigo byita ku bana, CDC isaba ko hashyirwaho igihe gito cyo gusukura cyangwa gusukura niba umuntu wafashwe n'iyo ndwara ari mu kigo cy'ishuri, hatitawe ku kuba yarakwirakwiriye mu baturage.
Iyo mu baturage hari igipimo gito cyangwa cy'ikibura cy'ubwandu, uburyo bwo kwirinda abantu, nko guhagarika ingendo zo mu mirima, amateraniro, n'andi materaniro manini nk'amasomo y'imyitozo ngororamubiri cyangwa amasomo y'abacuranzi cyangwa kurya mu kabari, kongera intera hagati y'ibiro, gutegura igihe cyo kuza no kugenda mu buryo butandukanye, kugabanya abasura batari ngombwa, no gukoresha ibiro by'ubuzima byitandukanyije ku bana bafite ibimenyetso bisa n'iby'ibicurane.
Iyo hari ubwandu bwinshi mu baturage, usibye ingamba zo kwirinda, kongera igihe cyo kuva mu ishuri bishobora kugenzurwa. Ku bakozi bashinzwe kubahiriza amategeko bakora imirimo isanzwe ya buri munsi, CDC ivuga ko ibyago by'ubuzima by'ibanze ari bike.
Abashinzwe kubahiriza amategeko bagomba kuvugana n'abantu bagaragayeho cyangwa bakekwaho kuba baranduye COVID-19 bagirwa inama yo gukurikiza amabwiriza nk'ay'abaganga b'ubutabazi, harimo n'ibikoresho bikwiye byo kwirinda.
Iyo habaye guhura mu buryo butaziguye mu gihe cyo gufunga, abakozi bagomba gusukura no gusukura imyenda n'ibikoresho by'akazi mbere yo kubikoresha bakoresheje imashini yo gusukura cyangwa isuku yo mu rugo, kandi bagakurikiza amabwiriza y'akazi yo guhangana n'umwanda, gutwika ibikoresho byo kwirinda bikoreshwa, gutoranya imyenda no kuyisukura.
Ikigo cy'Ubuzima n'Umutekano mu Mwuga gitekereza ko bamwe mu bakozi bo mu rwego rw'ubuzima n'abakora mu mirimo yo kubakira abapfuye, bashobora kuba bafite ibyago byinshi cyangwa byinshi byo kurwara.
Imirimo ifite ibyago byinshi harimo abakora mu by'ubuvuzi, mu bufasha, mu mavuriro no mu gutwara abantu, bagaragara ku barwayi bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19.
Iyo miterere y'ibyago iba iri hejuru cyane iyo abakozi bakora ibikorwa byo guhumeka umwuka, hamwe no gutoranya ibipimo by'abarwayi bemejwe ko banduye cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19 cyangwa se kubana na bo.
Mu bikorwa byo guhumeka umwuka harimo guteka, gukorora, gusuzuma amenyo, gukora ibizamini byo mu buvuzi bw'amenyo cyangwa gutoragura ibipimo by'imikorere y'amaraso.
Ibikorwa by'abafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura indwara ya COVID-19 birimo abakora mu gutegura imirambo y'abantu bizwi ko banduye cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19 igihe bapfuye; abo bantu baba bafite ibyago byinshi cyane iyo bakoze autopsies. Ibindi bikoresho by'ubwubatsi by'izi nzego z'abafite ibyago byinshi birimo ibyumba byo gutandukanya abarwayi bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19, harimo no gukora ibikorwa byo guhumeka umwuka.
Imyitozo yihariye yo guhumeka umwuka w'umuyaga ushobora kuba ari ingirakamaro mu bigo bimwe na bimwe byita ku buzima no mu kubika imirambo.
Ibipimo bigomba gufatwa hakurikijwe ingamba za Biosafety z'icyiciro cya 3.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryasabye ko abarwayi bagombaga kujya mu byumba by'akarere by'abarwayi batandukanye, hagendewe ku kuba bakekwaho COVID-19. Uretse ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi, ikigo cy'ubuzima n'umutekano mu kazi cyasabye ko abarwayi bakora mu ntera ya metero 6 uvuye ku barwayi bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho SARS-CoV-2, n'abakora ibikorwa byo guhumeka umwuka.
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, ibikoresho byo guhumeka bifite agapfukamunwa gafite isuzuma ry'ubwonko rya N95, ryemejwe n'Ikigo cy'Igihugu cy'Umutekano n'Ubuzima mu Mwuga, cyangwa ibindi bikoresho byiza, bigomba gukoreshwa mu rwego rw'umushinga w'ubwirinzi bw'ubuhumekero, urimo gupima uburyo bwo guhumeka, imyitozo n'ibizamini by'ubuvuzi.
Izindi bwoko z'ibikoresho byo guhumeka bishobora gutanga uburinzi bwinshi kandi bigatuma abakozi barushaho kugira ibyishimo. Umuryango w'Abibumbye wita ku buzima (OMS) ntutera inkunga gukoresha ibigo, kubera ko COVID-19 ari indwara yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero aho kuba ikwirakwira mu mazi yo mu mubiri.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryasabye ko abakozi ba siporo bakoresha agapfukamunwa mu gihe binjira mu gihugu gusa.
Ku bantu bakusanya ibipimo by'ubuhumekero by'abarwayi ba COVID-19, cyangwa babitaho, cyangwa babimura nta buryo bwo guhumeka, OMS isaba gukoresha agapfukamunwa, indorerwamo, cyangwa indorerwamo, imiruho n'indorerwamo.
Iyo habonetse umwuka wo mu kirere, agapfukamunwa gashyirwamo N95 cyangwa FFP2.
Kubera ko ibikoresho byo kwirinda umubiri ku isi byose bidahagije, OMS isaba ko hakorwa ingamba zo kugabanya ibyo bikoresho mu gihe umuntu ari kure, hakagira inzitizi z'umubiri nk'amadirishya asobanutse, byemerera gusa abita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 kwinjira mu cyumba, bakoresha ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi by'umubiri bikenewe gusa mu gihe cy'imikorere, bakomeza gukoresha agapfukamunwa k'ubuhumekero mu gihe bitabwaho abarwayi benshi bafite ibipimo bimwe, kandi bagakurikirana kandi bagashyira hamwe uburyo bwo gutanga ibikoresho byo kwirinda umubiri, kandi bakirinda gukoresha udupfukamunwa ku bantu badafite ibimenyetso.
