Enzyme ihindura angiotensin 2 (ACE2) ifata ku bice by'inyuma (ingingo z'ingirabuzimafatizo) z'ingirabuzimafatizo zo mu bihaha, mu mitsi, mu mutima, mu mpyiko no mu maraso.
Ingirabuzimafatizo ya angiotensin 2 ihangana n'ibikorwa bya angiotensin 2 (ACE) binyuze mu kugabanya ingano ya angiotensin 2 no kongera ingirabuzimafatizo (1-7), bigatuma iba umuti wizewe mu kuvura indwara z'umutima.
Imyandikire y'umuntu ya enzyme ikunze kwitwa hACE2.
Ingirabuzimafatizo ihindura angiotensin 2 ni ingirabuzimafatizo y'ibyuma irimo zinc, iba ku butaka bw'ingirabuzimafatizo z'uruhu n'izindi.
Poroteyine ya enzyme ihindura angiotensin 2 ifite uruhande rwa peptidase M2 ifite amino-terminus, na colectreini-chain carboxyl-terminus ari yo itwara amino acid z'impyiko.
Angiotensin 2 ni poroteyine y'uruhu rumwe yo mu bwoko bwa 1, ifite intangabuzima za enzyme zikorera ku maso y'ingirabuzimafatizo z'ibihaha n'izindi.
Igice cyo hanze y'uruziga cya angiotensin 2 gihindura ingirabuzimafatizo gitandukanywa n'uruziga binyuze mu kibuno na enzyme yitwa Shidas, ituma haboneka poroteyine ishobora gushonga mu maraso hanyuma ikava mu cyondo.
Ingirabuzimafatizo ihindura angiotensin 2 iboneka mu bice byinshi by'umubiri: ifata mu gice cy'ingirabuzimafatizo z'amaraso zo mu bwoko bwa 2 mu bihaha, mu bice by'amaraso yo mu maraso mato, mu bice by'amaraso byo mu mitsi no mu mitsi, no mu bice by'umubiri byinshi.
ADN yoherezwa n'umuti uhindura angiotensin 2 iboneka mu gice cy'ubwonko, mu gice cy'ubwonko, mu gice cy'ubwonko kiri munsi y'urwego rw'ubwonko, no mu gice cy'ubwonko.
Umurimo w'ibanze wa angiotensin 2 ni ugukora nk'umuhuza wa angiotensin 2.
Enzyme ihindura angiotensin ituma habaho guhindura ingirabuzimafatizo ya angiotensin 1 ikavamo angiotensin 2 ifata ingufu z'amaraso.
Mu gihe ingirabuzimafatizo ihindura angiotensin 2 ifite karuboksile igize amino acid yitwa vinyl alanine, itandukanya angiotensin 2 (aspartate-arginine-valine-tyrosine-isoleucine-histidine-proline-phenyl alanine) ikabihindura angiotensin (1-7), (histidine-aspartate-arginine-valine-tyrosine-isoleucine-histidine-proline-phenyl alanine).
Iyi enzyme ihindura angiotensin 2 isobanura indi mibonano itandukanye harimo [dis-arginine9] - bradricenin, ablenine, neurotensin, adenorphine A, na gerlen.
Iyi enzyme ihindura angiotensin 2 nayo igenzura uruhu rw'umuyoboro wa SLC6A19, kandi igira uruhare mu ndwara ya Hartnup.
Ingirabuzimafatizo ihindura angiotensin 2, nk'umushongi w'uruhu, ni inzira y'ibanze yinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo za coronavirusi zimwe na zimwe, zirimo virusi ya HCoV NL63, SARS-CoV (virusi itera SARS-CoV-2), na SARS-CoV-2 (virusi itera COVID-19).
By'umwihariko, gusangira poroteyine ya S1 spike ya SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 na enzyme ya angiotensin 2 ku isura y'ingirabuzimafatizo bituma ingirabuzimafatizo zigenda zikora, zikajya mu bice by'imbere mu ngirabuzimafatizo.
Iyi gahunda yo kwinjiza ikenera ko poroteyine ya S ihindurwa na serine2 ikora mu mubiri, ikaba ikiri mu igeragezwa nk'umuti ushobora kuvura iyi ndwara. Ibyo bituma bamwe batekereza ko kugabanya ingano ya angiotensin 2 mu ngirabuzimafatizo bishobora gufasha kurwanya indwara.
Icyakora, imiryango myinshi y'abahanga n'inzego zishinzwe kwiyobora zemeza ko hakwiye gukomeza gukoreshwa imiti isanzwe yo kurwanya ingirabuzimafatizo za angiotensin, hamwe n'imiti ituma umuntu atabona ingirabuzimafatizo za angiotensin.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku buryo bufatika no ku buryo bwo gusuzuma imiterere y'umubiri, bwashyizwe ahagaragara ku itariki ya 11 Nyakanga 2012, bwagaragaje ko "gukoresha imiti ituma umuntu atakaza ingirabuzima fatizo yitwa angiotensin byari bifitanye isano no kugabanya cyane ibyago byo kurwara indwara y'ibihaha ku kigero cya 34 ku ijana ugereranyije n'itsinda ry'abagereranyije".
Byongeye kandi, "abafashwe na angiotensin-metabolism inhibitors bari bafite ibyago byo kurwara indwara y'ibicurane byagabanutse, cyane cyane abafite indwara yo kuva mu bwonko cyangwa umutima udakora neza.
Gukoresha imiti ituma umuntu atakaza ingirabuzimafatizo yitwa angiotensin byagabanyije umubare w'abapfa bazize indwara z'ibicurane, nubwo ibyo byagize ingaruka nke ugereranyije n'ingaruka rusange zo kurwara indwara z'ibicurane".
Igisukari cy'umuntu cyitwa angiotensin 2 (rhACE2) giteganyijwe ko kizaba umuti mushya wo kuvura indwara z'ibihaha by'umuriro.
Ingingo ya 2 ihindura angiotensin ifite ubuzima bw'igice cy'isaha igera ku 10, ikora nyuma y'iminota 30, kandi ikora amasaha 24.
Hari ibimenyetso byinshi bigaragaza ko ingirabuzimafatizo ya angiotensin 2 ishobora kuba umuti wizewe ku bantu batagaragaza ubukana bw'imiti ya angiotensin 2 mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga (RAS inhibitors), no mu ndwara zifitanye isano no kugira ingirabuzimafatizo ya angiotensin 2 mu maraso. Hari n'ibizamini by'ubushakashatsi biri gukorwa ku ngaruka zo guterwa ingirabuzimafatizo ya angiotensin 2 mu kuvura indwara yo guhungabana k'ubuhumekero (AAPS).
Porogaramu za COVID-19 ni porogaramu za porogaramu zigendanwa zashyizweho mu buryo bwihariye kugira ngo zifashe gukurikirana abantu banduye mu gisubizo cy'icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019-20, bivuze ko ari igikorwa cyo kumenya abantu ("abanduye") bashobora kuba baranduye umuntu.
Hariho porogaramu nyinshi zateguwe cyangwa zatangajwe zifashishijwe na leta mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe.
Hariho uburyo bwinshi bwo gukora porogaramu zo gukurikirana abakoze ibyaha.
Abantu benshi bagaragaje impungenge ku bijyanye n'ibanga, cyane cyane ku bijyanye n'uburyo bwo gukurikirana aho abakoresha porogaramu bari.
Ibindi byoroshye harimo gukoresha Bluetooth kugira ngo umuntu ashobore kubona amakuru y'aho ari.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple byatangaje ko byashyize hamwe imikorere ishyigikira izi porogaramu zishingiye kuri Bluetooth, mu buryo butaziguye muri sisitemu z'imikorere za Android na iOS.
Mu Bushinwa, leta y'Ubushinwa ifatanyije na Alipay, yashyizeho porogaramu ituma abaturage bashobora kureba niba barigeze kuvugana n'abantu banduye COVID-19.
Ni porogaramu ikoreshwa n'abantu ku giti cyabo mu mijyi 200 yo mu Bushinwa. Muri Singapuru, abantu bakoresha porogaramu yitwa TraceTogether.
Ikigo cy'igihugu cy'ikoranabuhanga mu by'amakuru cyakoze igishushanyo mbonera cy'iyi porogaramu, igashyirwa hanze nk'umushinga ukoreshwa n'abantu bose kandi ugiye gushyikirizwa leta. Macédoine y'Amajyaruguru yatangije porogaramu ya "StopKorona", ikoreshwa na Bluetooth mu gukurikirana abantu bashobora kuba barwaye indwara z'ibicurane no gutanga ibisubizo byihuse ku nzego z'ubuzima.
Minisiteri y'itumanaho n'ikoranabuhanga yakoranye na Minisiteri y'ubuzima mu gukora iyi porogaramu.
Ku ya 14 Mata 2020, iyi porogaramu yari ikirindiriye kwemerwa na Google Play Store na App Store ya Apple.
Ku ya 12 Mata, leta yavuze ko porogaramu yo gukurikirana abantu bakwirakwizaga virusi itera imbere, kandi ko ishobora kuzaboneka mu byumweru bike. Ireland n'u Bufaransa na byo biteganya gutangiza porogaramu nk'iyo, yitwa "StopCovid".
Australia na Nouvelle Zélande byombi birimo gutekereza ku gukora porogaramu zishingiye kuri TraceTogether yatangijwe na Singapore, hamwe na BlueTrees.Russian.Ibikorwa byo gutangiza porogaramu ikoresha imiterere ya geo-virtual ku barwayi bagaragaweho COVID-19 n'abaganga baba i Moscou, byateganyijwe ku buryo batashobora kuva mu rugo.
Ross Anderson, umwarimu muri kaminuza ya Cambridge wigisha iby'umutekano, yavuze ibibazo byinshi bishobora kuvuka ku mikorere y'ibikoresho, harimo n'ibimenyetso by'uko byashoboraga gukoreshwa n'abantu bake.
Mu guhangana n'impungenge z'ikwirakwira ry'imikorere ya virusi ya Corona ibeshya cyangwa yangiza, Apple yashyizeho imipaka ku byerekeye ubwoko bw'imiryango ishobora kongeramo porogaramu zayo zijyanye na virusi ya Corona ku iduka ry'imikoreshereze yayo; ibi byateganijwe gusa ku miryango "yemewe" cyangwa indi ifite izina ryiza.
Google na Amazon na byo byashyizeho ingamba nk'izo.
Abashyigikiye ubuzima bwite bagaragaje impungenge ku ngaruka zo kugenzura abantu benshi hakoreshejwe porogaramu za virusi ya corona, cyane cyane niba ibikorwa remezo by'iperereza byakozwe mu guhangana n'icyorezo cya virusi ya corona bizashira vuba.
Amnesty International n'andi mashyirahamwe asaga 100 yasohoye itangazo risaba ko habaho ingamba zo kugabanya ubwo buryo bwo kugenzura.
Imiryango kandi yatangaje ibintu umunani by'ibanze by'imishinga ya leta:
Gucunga abantu bigomba kuba "binyuranyije n'amategeko, bikenewe kandi bihuje n'imimerere";
Amasezerano yo kugenzura no kugenzura agomba kuba arimo ingingo zigena igihe cyo kuyakuraho;
Gukoresha amakuru bigomba kuba bigenewe gusa COVID-19;
Umutekano n'ibanga by'amakuru bigomba kurindwa kandi bigakorwa hashingiwe ku bimenyetso;
Igenzura ry'ibaruramari rigomba kwirinda ko habaho ivangura no kwirengagizwa;
Gutanga amakuru ku bandi bigomba gushyirwa mu mategeko;
Ibikoresho byo kurinda ihohoterwa no kurinda uburenganzira bw'abaturage bigomba kuboneka kugira ngo hakorwe ibikorwa byo kurwanya ihohoterwa;
"Kwifatanya mu buryo bugira ingaruka nziza" birasabwa n' "abafite uruhare bose", harimo n'impuguke mu by'ubuzima rusange n'amatsinda y'abasizwe. Chaos Computer Club (CCC) yo mu Budage na Reporter ohne Grenzen (RSF) na zo zatangaje urutonde rw'ibyagiye bigenzurwa.
Gahunda ya Google/Apple igamije gukemura ikibazo cy'uburinzi buhoraho, ikuraho uburyo bwo gukurikirana ibikoresho mu buryo bwa sisitemu zikora igihe bikimara gukoreshwa.
Ibihugu bimwe na bimwe byakoresheje uburyo bwo gukurikirana aho umuntu ari hakoreshejwe imbuga nkoranyambaga aho gukoresha porogaramu, ibyo bikaba byaratumye abantu bataba bakeneye kuzikuraho, kandi bigatuma abantu bashobora kwirinda gukurikiranwa.
Muri Isirayeli, abategetsi bashyizeho uburyo bwo gukurikirana abantu hakoreshejwe imbuga nkoranyambaga.
Ariko, ibisubizo bishingiye ku mbuga za interineti bifite uburyo bwo kubona amakuru y'ibanze yerekeye imyanya, bishobora guteza ibibazo bikomeye by'ibanga.
Icyakora, si ko buri sisitemu yose ifite seriveri z'ibanze ikenera kubona amakuru y'aho umuntu ari; hari sisitemu nyinshi zo kubungabunga ubuzima bwite zashyizweho zikoresha seriveri z'ibanze gusa mu itumanaho (reba igice gikurikira).
Muri Koreya y'Epfo, abategetsi bakoresheje uburyo butari bwo bushingiye kuri porogaramu kugira ngo bakurikirane abakora ibikorwa byo guhungabanya ibidukikije.
Aho gukoresha porogaramu yihariye, iyi sisitemu ikusanya amakuru yo gukurikirana mu buryo butandukanye, harimo amakuru yo gukurikirana ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga n'amakuru y'ubucuruzi bw'ikarita, kandi ikayashyira hamwe kugira ngo yohereze imenyesha binyuze mu butumwa bw'ibaruwa ku bantu bashobora kuba barwaye.
Usibye gukoresha aya makuru mu kuburira abantu bashobora kuba bakoresha amakuru, leta yatumye aya makuru agera ku bantu bose, kubera ko amategeko agenga ubuzima bwite bw'abantu yahindutse cyane nyuma y'icyorezo cya Coronavirus.
Aya makuru aboneka ku mugaragaro binyuze muri porogaramu nyinshi na interineti. Ibihugu, harimo n'u Budage, byatekereje gukoresha uburyo bwa centralization n'ubwirinzi bw'ibanga.
Ku ya 6 Mata 2020, amakuru arambuye kuri iki kibazo ntabwo yari yaratangajwe.
Abashakashatsi mu by'ibanga bafite igitekerezo cy'ibanga kandi cy'ibanze cy'ibanga, cyashyigikiwe n'ubushakashatsi bukomeye bwabayeho mu mwaka wa 2013. Ku itariki ya 7 Mata 2020, amatsinda y'impuguke asaga icumi yakoranye kugira ngo agere ku bisubizo bihuza n'ibanga, urugero nka Bluetooth ifite ingufu nke (BLE) kugira ngo ashobore gufata amajwi y'abakoresha telefoni z'imbere.
