Mu cyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2, ubu bushakashatsi bwibanda ku poroteyine ya SPICS ifasha virusi kwinjira mu byuma bikira ACE2.
Uburyo bwa gatatu ni urukingo rwa ADN (uru rukingo rwa RNA cyangwa RNA, ni ikoranabuhanga rishya ryo gukora urukingo).
Inkingo z'igerageza ziterwa n'ubwo buryo bwagenewe kugerageza zigomba kugeragezwa kugira ngo zimenyekane ko ari nziza kandi ko zikora neza. Ku itariki ya 16 Werurwe 2020, inkingo ya mbere yo kwivuza yatangiriye ku bantu bane bitangiye gukora imirimo i Seattle.
Uru rukingo rufite kode ya jenoside itagira ingaruka ya virusi iteza indwara. Kwongera imbaraga z'umubiri w'umuntu byerekanwa nk'imbogamizi ishobora guhangana n'ikoranabuhanga ry'urukingo rwa SARS-CoV-2, ariko ibyo ni impaka.
Hari ibizamini by'ubuvuzi birenga 300 birimo gukorwa guhera muri Mata 2020.
Hariho ibizamini birindwi by'ubuvuzi bwa malaria byamaze kwemerwa, harimo n'ibyiciro bine by'ubuvuzi bwa hydroxychloroquine cyangwa chlorquine.
Imiti ya antiviral igamije kongera gukoreshwa mu kuvura indwara nshya ni yo ikoreshwa cyane mu bushakashatsi bw'Abashinwa, mu igerageza ry'icyiciro cya gatatu ry'icyiciro cya cyenda rya Remdesivir mu bihugu byinshi, rigomba gutangwa mu mpera za Mata.
Igenzura ry'imiterere y'imiti n'imiti ya COVID-19 byakozwe kuva muri Mata 2020. Imiti myinshi ya antiviral ikoreshwa mu kuvura COVID-19 irimo gusuzumwa, harimo Remdesivir, chlorokine, hydroxychloroquine, lupinavir/ritonavir na lupinavir/tonavir ifatanyije na interverone beta.
Hari ibimenyetso by'ibanze bigaragaza ko Remdesivir ikora, kuva muri Werurwe 2020.
Mu barwayi bavurwa umuti wa Remdesivir ukoreshwa mu gihe cy'imibonano mpuzabitsina, habonetse ubwiyongere mu buriri.
Ibizamini by'icyiciro cya gatatu birimo gukorwa muri Amerika, Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani. Ikoreshwa rya chlorokine mu kuvura malariya, ryashyizwe mu bushakashatsi mu Bushinwa muri Gashyantare 2020, kandi rigira ingaruka za mbere.
Icyakora, hari abantu basabye ko ubushakashatsi bukorwa n'abandi bantu.
Abayobozi b'ubuzima bo muri Koreya no mu Bushinwa batanga inama yo gukoresha chlorokine.
Nyamara, Ikigo cya Wuhan cy'Ubushakashatsi ku Virusi kigaragaza ko nubwo hatangwa urugero rw'igarama imwe, kugabanya urugero rw'iyo miti bishobora guteza akaga gakomeye kandi bishobora no gutuma umuntu apfa.
Ku ya 28 Werurwe 2020, FDA yatanze uruhushya rw'ubutabazi bw'ibicurane bya hydroxychloroquine na chloroquine mu gihe abaganga bavura abantu barwaye COVID-19.
Amakuru y'ibanze agaragaza ko imiti yo mu rwego rwo hejuru ya ribavirin ari ngombwa kugira ngo SARS-CoV-2 ihagarare mu kigo cy'ubushakashatsi.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe bwagaragaje ko gutangiza poroteyine ya spike binyuze muri protease ya trans-membrane serine 2 (TMPRSS2) ari ngombwa kugira ngo SARS-CoV-2 yinjire binyuze mu guhuza na ACES2.
Ubushakashatsi ku miti ya chlorokine na hydroxychloroquine hamwe na azithromycin cyangwa ntayo bufite, bufite amakosa menshi yatumye umuryango w'ubuvuzi udashobora kwemera iyi miti nta kindi cyifuzo. Oseltamivir ntabwo ihagarika SARS-CoV-2 muri laboratwari kandi nta ruhare ifite mu kuvura COVID-19.
Umuyaga w'ibinyabutabire ushobora kuba ari kimwe mu bibazo by'indwara ya COVID-19 iri mu bihe bya nyuma.
Hari ibimenyetso bigaragaza ko hydroxychloroquine ishobora kugira ubushobozi bwo kurwanya cytocin storm. Komisiyo y'igihugu y'ubuzima mu Bushinwa yongeye tuzilisumab mu mabwiriza y'ubuvuzi nyuma yo gukora ubushakashatsi buto.
Ni icyiciro cya 2 cy'igerageza ry'ubushakashatsi mu rwego rw'igihugu mu Butaliyani nyuma yo kugaragaza ko abantu barwaye indwara zikomeye bafite ibimenyetso by'indwara.
Uretse kuba ikoreshwa mu gupima feritini mu maraso kugira ngo hamenyekane ibihuha bya sitokine, igamije kurwanya ibyo bintu by'ingenzi, byibwira ko ari byo bituma abantu bamwe bapfa.
FDA yemeje interleukin-6 anti-receptor, ubuvuzi bwa T-cell receptor ya anti-Kymeric, ishingiye ku nyigo z'ibyigwa byo gusubiza inyuma mu kuvura syndrome yo kuvanaho sitokine ku bantu batitabira steroid bafite impamvu itandukanye mu 2017.
Kugeza ubu, nta gihamya yemewe yemeza ko tosilezumab ari umuti w'ingirakamaro wo kuvura sitokini.
Uburyo bwo gutanga za antibodies zitunganyijwe kandi ziganjemo cyane ziterwa n'imikorere y'umubiri w'abantu bakize COVID-19 ku bantu babikeneye, buzakorwaho ubushakashatsi nk'uburyo butari ubw'inkingo bwo gutera inda.
Ubwo buryo bwageragejwe kuri SARS kandi nta cyizere cy'uko bwagiraga icyo bugeraho.
Kugabanya virusi ni uburyo bwo gukora buteganyijwe aho umuti w'umubiri utandura ushobora gukoreshwa nk'umuhuza mu kwirwanaho kuri SARS-CoV-2.
Ariko kandi, hari ubundi buryo bushobora gukoreshwa, urugero nk'uburozi bw'ingirabuzimafatizo cyangwa uburozi bw'amaraso cyangwa byombi.
Hari ubundi buryo bwo kuvura antibodies zidakira, urugero nko gukoresha antibodies z'ubwoko bumwe zikozwe mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga, burimo gukorwa.
Dushobora kongera ingano ya serum ya renin, igizwe n'igice cy'umunyunyu w'amaraso y'abarwayi bakize, kandi ikaba irimo udukoko tw'ubwirinzi bwihariye kuri iyi virusi, kugira ngo tuyikwirakwize vuba.
